2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1715013792697045503%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaw%20enforcement%20seized%2032%20phones%2C%2048%20laptops%20and%20hard%20discs%2C%20and%2033%20SIM%20cards%20and%20froze%20several%20bank%20accounts%20amid%20the%20raid%20of%20the%2076%20locations%2C%20according%20to%20CBI.%20The%20locations%20were%20in%20Indian%20states%20including%20Bihar%2C%20Dehli%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%20%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIkREEmr0maw%3Fsi%3DB951S6KHHwjPvFyZ%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpdf.live%2Fedit%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ic3.gov%252FMedia%252FPDF%252FAnnualReport%252F2022_IC3Report.pdf%26guid%3D2ddc7657-c83a-6076-17bc-72ec9ddcb2b2%26installDate%3D070723%26source%3Dgoogle-d_pdftab_crx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFBI%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimates%20that%20in%202022%2C%20over%2032%2C000%20people%20were%20targeted%20by%20tech%20and%20customer%20support%20scams%2C%20with%20over%20%24800%20million%20in%20losses.%20Amazon%20said%20it%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero%20tolerance%26quot%3B%20policy%20for%20scammers%20pretending%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20company.%20It%20has%20taken%20down%20over%2020%2C000%20phishing%20websites%20and%2010%2C000%20phone%20numbers%20associated%20with%20fraud%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOftentimes%2C%20scammers%20will%20target%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-its-so-easy-to-scam-old-people-2012-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelderly%