%E2%80%9Chigh-level%20inquiry%20committee%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20look%20into%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20two%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20even%20as%20a%20Hindtuva%20group%2C%20Hindu%20Raksha%20Dal%2C%20had%20announced%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20faculty%20member%20who%20had%20asked%20the%20student%20to%20step%20down%2C%20Kumar%20posted%20another%20video%20on%20Instagram%20to%20announce%20that%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20two%20teachers%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinappropriate%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20the%20committee%20was%20asked%20to%20submit%20their%20recommendations%20within%2024%20hours%20which%20it%20adhered%20to.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20its%20recommendation%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20suspend%20the%20services%20of%20the%20two%20faculty%20members%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20teachers%20have%20not%20pleaded%20guilty.%20One%20of%20the%20suspended%20teachers%2C%20Mamta%20Gautam%2C%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20that%20she%20was%20not%20opposed%20to%20chanting%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20but%20the%20student%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20stage%20because%20he%20was%20arguing%20with%20her.%20%E2%80%9CHighlighting%20her%20%E2%80%98Sanatani%E2%80%99%20roots%2C%20the%20teacher%20says%20she%20is%20being%20targeted%20by%20an%20online%20mob%2C%E2%80%9D%20New18%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Fabes-college-jai-shri-ram-controversy-vira-video-updates-ghaziabad-professor-suspended-mamata-gautam-india-news-8628068.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20local%20police%20have%20told%20some%20TV%20channels%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cinvestigating%20the%20matter%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csuitable%20action%20would%20be%20taken%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697894165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21183802%2FThe-Wire-47.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fghaziabad-college-two-teachers-suspended-for-asking-student-to-leave-stage-over-jai-shri-ram-slogan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20suspended%20teachers%20said%20she%20was%20not%20opposed%20to%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogan%2C%20but%20she%20asked%20the%20student%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20stage%20as%20he%20allegedly%20argued%20with%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fghaziabad-college-two-teachers-suspended-for-asking-student-to-leave-stage-over-jai-shri-ram-slogan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Sindhu%20In%20Verbal%20Duel%20vs%20Marin%20In%20Ill-Tempered%20Denmark%20Open%20Match%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStruggling%20Indian%20shuttler%20PV%20Sindhu%20lost%20to%20her%20old%20nemesis%20Carolina%20Marin%20of%20Spain%20in%20three%20games%20in%20an%20ill-tempered%20semifinal%20of%20the%20Denmark%20Open%20Super%20750%20tournament%2C%20which%20saw%20both%20players%20receive%20yellow%20cards%20for%20verbal%20exchanges%2C%20Odense%20(Denmark%20on%20Saturday.%20Sindhu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20struggling%20the%20whole%20season%2C%20lost%2018-21%2C%2021-19%2C%207-21%20in%20the%20match%20that%20lasted%20one%20hour%20and%2013%20minutes.%20This%20was%20Sindhu's%20fifth%20loss%20on%20the%20trot%20against%20Marin%20who%20had%20beaten%20the%20Indian%20in%20that%20memorable%202016%20Rio%20Olympics%20final%20as%20well%20as%20the%202018%20World%20Championships%20summit%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorld%20number%2012%20Sindhu%20and%20Marin%2C%20currently%20ranked%20sixth%2C%20had%20earlier%20talked%20about%20good%20camaraderie%20between%20them%20but%20they%20showed%20none%20of%20it%20on%20the%20court%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20were%20warned%20verbally%20by%20the%20umpire%20multiple%20times%20before%20being%20shown%20yellow%20cards%20in%20the%20deciding%20game.%20The%20umpire%20initially%20called%20both%20the%20players%20to%20tone%20down%20their%20celebrations%20after%20winning%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EYellow%20card%20for%20both%20Marin%20and%20Sindhu%20Dramatic%20scene%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDenmarkOpen2023%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DenmarkOpen2023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjMYuUYRqf4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjMYuUYRqf4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Twee%20Twee%20(%40ThongWeeDaphne)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThongWeeDaphne%2Fstatus%2F1715692453703913760%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Marin%20continued%20to%20scream%20and%20celebrate%20while%20Sindhu%20was%20warned%20twice%20for%20taking%20longer%20time%20in%20receiving%20serve.%20Marin%20was%20warned%20twice%20for%20loud%20celebrations%20after%20taking%20the%20first%20game%2021-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20decider%20after%20Sindhu%20won%20the%20second%20game%2C%20the%20umpire%20warned%20the%20Indian%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20receive%20serve%20quickly.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20Sinhdu%20was%20heard%20saying%20'you%20allowed%20her%20to%20shout%2C%20so%20you%20ask%20her%20and%20then%20I%20will%20be%20ready'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20after%20that%2C%20the%20shuttle%20fell%20on%20Sindhu's%20court%20and%20both%20reached%20to%20pick%20it%2C%20leading%20to%20another%20verbal%20altercation.%20The%20chair%20umpire%20called%20both%20the%20players%20and%20flashed%20yellow%20cards%20to%20them.%20Marin%20was%20also%20told%20not%20to%20pick%20shuttle%20from%20Sindhu's%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20game%2C%20the%20two%20were%20locked%203-3%20and%20then%207-7.%20Moments%20of%20brilliance%20were%20followed%20by%20odd%20errors%20from%20both%20as%20the%20score%20read%2018-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Spaniard%20then%20unleashed%20a%20body%20smash%20and%20grabbed%20two%20games%20points%20when%20Sindhu's%20backhand%20hit%20the%20net%20and%20followed%20it%20with%20a%20powerful%20smash%20to%20earn%20the%20bragging%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESindhu%2C%20who%20had%20famously%20hugged%20Marin%20after%20the%20Rio%20Olympics%20final%20defeat%2C%20had%20a%20solid%20strength%20to%20the%20second%20game%2C%20leading%206-2.%20The%20Indian%20zoomed%2010-3%20ahead%20as%20she%20showed%20better%20control%20at%20the%20net%2C%20while%20Marin%20was%20too%20erratic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20interval%2C%20Marin%20took%20the%20initiative%20and%20soon%20the%20rallies%20got%20shorter%20and%20faster%20with%20the%20Spaniard%20producing%20the%20winners%20with%20solid%20net-play.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESindhu%20ended%20a%20stretch%20of%20seven%20straight%20points%20after%20winning%20a%20fast%20exchange%20to%20maintain%20the%2012-10%20lead.%20Sindhu%20then%20had%20four%20game%20points%20at%2020-16.%20Marin%20saved%20three%20before%20Sindhu%20sealed%20it%20with%20a%20smash%20to%20take%20the%20match%20to%20the%20decider.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Marin%20who%20took%20the%20initiative%20in%20the%20decider%2C%20moving%20to%203-0%20and%20then%208-2.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarin%20was%2014-3%20up%20and%20around%20that%20time%20both%20were%20shown%20yellow%20cards%20for%20engaging%20in%20a%20verbal%20duel.%20The%20incident%20seemed%20to%20rattle%20Sindhu%20as%20nothing%20went%20her%20way%20and%20it%20was%20one%20way%20traffic.%20Soon%2C%20Marin%20ended%20Sindhu's%20misery%20after%20having%2013%20match%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESindhu%20had%20also%20reached%20the%20semifinals%20at%20the%20Arctic%20Open%20Super%20500%20last%20week%20in%20Finland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A16978