%20leader%20along%20with%20nine%20of%20his%20aides%20is%20detained%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20(NSA).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22YUDHVIR%20RANA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Famritsar%2Fpro-khalistan-preacher-amritpal-singh-gets-permission-to-meet-new-lawyer-in-assam-jail%2Farticleshow%2F104611265.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAttempts%20Made%20To%20Coerce...%26quot%3B%3A%20Advocate%20Writes%20To%20Cops%20In%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20who%20had%20written%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20a%20BJP%20MP%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20evidence%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20accepting%20bribes%20from%20a%20businessman%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%2C%20has%20now%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20commissioner%20claiming%20that%20he%20anticipates%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20serious%20threat%20to%20his%20life%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20has%20also%20claimed%20a%20direct%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20coerce%20him%20into%20withdrawing%20his%20complaint%20and%20threats%20of%20harming%20his%20reputation%20were%20made%20if%20he%20did%20not%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dehadrai%2C%20who%20Ms%20Moitra%20has%20called%20her%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20reportedly%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20and%20the%20two%20have%20allegedly%20not%20been%20on%20the%20best%20terms%20since%20they%20parted%20ways.%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20friction%20between%20them%20is%20their%20pet%20dog%2C%20a%20Rottweiler%20named%20Henry.%20Both%20have%20accused%20the%20other%20of%20'stealing'%20Henry%20and%20a%20battle%20for%20his%20custody%20is%20being%20fought%20in%20court.%20The%20dog%20is%20currently%20with%20Ms%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20to%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Arora%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20has%20said%20he%20was%20writing%20under%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20distressing%20circumstances%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20anticipating%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life%20because%20of%20his%20complaint%20dated%20October%2014%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%20and%20others%2C%20which%20he%20had%20submitted%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20to%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20alleged%20that%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20a%20direct%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20coerce%20him%20into%20withdrawing%20his%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThreats%20of%20reputational%20harm%20were%20also%20conveyed%20in%20case%20I%20did%20not%20agree.%20The%20very%20specific%20demand%20was%20that%20I%20should%20unconditionally%20withdraw%20both%20the%20complaints%20in%20which%20very%20serious%20allegations%20pertaining%20to%20national%20security%20and%20corruption%20have%20been%20alleged%20by%20me%20against%20Smt.%20Moitra%20and%20others.%20It%20was%20stated%20that%20my%20pet%20Rottweiler%20Henry%20would%20be%20returned%20by%20Ms.%20Moitra%20to%20me%20if%20I%20agreed%20to%20withdraw%20the%20said%20complaints%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Pressured%20A%20Cop'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dehadrai%20alleged%20that%20his%20concerns%20were%20serious%2C%20given%20the%20Trinamool%20MP's%20%E2%80%9Chistory%20of%20misusing%20her%20influence%20and%20political%20clout%20to%20browbeat%20and%20intimidate%20opponents%E2%80%9D.%20%C2%A0He%20claimed%20that%20she%20had%20attempted%20to%20%E2%80%9Cextort%E2%80%9D%20Henry%20from%20him%20by%20filing%20two%20%E2%80%9Cbogus%E2%80%9D%20complaints%20against%20him%20with%20the%20Barakhamba%20Road%20Police%20Station%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20pressured%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%20of%20the%20police%20station%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbrowbeat%20him%20into%20giving%20up%20the%20lawful%20ownership%20of%20Henry%E2%80%9D%20over%20to%20her.%20He%20claimed%20the%20policeman%20was%20innocent%20as%20he%20was%20being%20%E2%80%9Cthreatened%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20but%20said%20that%20he%20must%20come%20clean%20on%20his%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20succumbed%20and%20sent%20Henry%20to%20Smt.%20Moitra%20on%2004.10.2023%2C%20she%20immediately%20signed%20a%20letter%20not%20only%20unconditionally%20withdrawing%20her%20so-called%20complaints%20against%20me%2C%20but%20also%20explicitly%20asking%20the%20police%20not%20to%20take%20any%20action%20against%20me.%20Thus%2C%20given%20the%20extremely%20dangerous%20and%20dubious%20antecedents%20of%20Ms.%20Moitra%20and%20her%20accomplices%2C%20I%20anticipate%20an%20attack%20on%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20lawyer%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Attempts%20To%20Stop%20Me%20From%20Deposing'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20said%20he%20was%20apprehensive%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%20quarters%E2%80%9D%20might%20attempt%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20deposing%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%20on%20October%2026%20as%20well%20as%20before%20investigating%20agencies.%20To%20back%20up%20this%20claim%2C%20he%20said%20he%20had%20received%20several%20%E2%80%9Cstrange%20messages%E2%80%9D%20from%20unknown%20numbers%20on%20his%20personal%20phone%20as%20well%20as%20three%20phone%20calls%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9CNo%20Caller%20ID%E2%80%9D%20number%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20strange%20occurrences%20that%20have%20been%20going%20on%2C%20I%20fear%20for%20the%20well-being%20of%20my%20Chamber%20colleagues%20and%20myself.%20As%20I%20possess%20extremely%20sensitive%20evidence%20and%20material%20pertaining%20to%20this%20case%2C%20there%20is%20every%20likelihood%20that%20attempts%20could%20be%20made%20to%20either%20destroy%20this%20material%20or%20obtain%20it%20from%20me%20under%20threat%20of%20bodily%20harm.%20I%20therefore%20humbly%20request%20you%20to%20assess%20the%20threats%20in%20question%20and%20provide%20adequate%20protection%2C%20as%20you%20deem%20fit%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20stated.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697893320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fhfj614pk_mahua-moitra_625x300_20_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempts-made-to-coerce-advocate-writes-to-cops-in-mahua-moitra-case-4502793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20who%20had%20written%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20a%20BJP%20MP%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20evidence%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20accepting%20bribes%20from%20a%20businessman%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%2C%20has%20now%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempts-made-to-coerce-advocate-writes-to-cops-in-mahua-moitra-case-4502793%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempts-made-to-coerce-advocate-writes-to-cops-in-mahua-moitra-case-4502793%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fattempts-made-to-coerce-advocate-writes-to-cops-in-mahua-moitra-case-4502793%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GRAP%20'Stage%20II'%20measures%20implemented%20as%20Delhi-NCR%20brace%20for%20'very%20poor'%20AQI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697893082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104611615%2Cimgsize-16570.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-ncr-brace-for-very-poor-air-quality-as-centre-implements-grap-stage-ii-measures%2Farticleshow%2F104611231.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre's%20air%20quality