ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstd-infection-rates-may-be-on-rise-during-coronavirus-pandemic-2020-5%5C%22%3ESTIs%20are%20on%20the%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20doxy-PEP%20within%2072%20hours%20of%20unprotected%20sex%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20help%20anyone%20concerned%20about%20their%20risk%20of%20bacterial%20STIs%2C%20including%20chlamydia%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-gonorrhea-is-antibiotic-resistant-2018-5%5C%22%3Egonorrhea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20syphilis%2C%20doctors%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20this%20summer%2C%20Dr.%20Laura%20Purdy%2C%20chief%20medical%20officer%20at%20Wisp%2C%20has%20been%20offering%20the%20antibiotic%20to%20patients%20of%20all%20genders%20and%20orientations%20who%20are%20concerned%20about%20contracting%20a%20bacterial%20STI%20after%20unprotected%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20treatment%20is%20crucial%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsexually-transmitted-disease-std-covid-19-made-worse-experts-2021-10%5C%22%3Ereducing%20bacterial%20STI%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Purdy%20told%20Insider%20by%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESTI%20reduction%20in%20high-risk%20groups%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDoxycycline%20was%20approved%20in%201967%20and%20has%20since%20been%20used%20to%20treat%20bacterial%20infections%20ranging%20from%20acne%20to%20malaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20studies%20have%20found%20it%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fgonorrhea-syphilis-cases-out-of-control-in-us-std-expert-2022-9%5C%22%3Ereduce%20STI%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20certain%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2211934%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20The%20New%20England%20Journal%20of%20Medicine%20earlier%20this%20year%20found%20that%20doxy-PEP%20reduced%20the%20risk%20for%20STIs%20like%20chlamydia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combined%20risk%20for%20chlamydia%2C%20syphilis%2C%20and%20gonorrhea%20was%20reduced%20by%20two-thirds%20in%20participants%20who%20took%20doxy-PEP%20compared%20to%20those%20who%20did%20not%2C%20the%20researchers%20reported%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20worth%20noting%20the%20study%20focused%20on%20high-risk%20populations%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftrans-woman-saving-money-gender-affirming-care-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrans%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20men%20who%20have%20sex%20with%20men%20who%20were%20already%20on%20PrEP%20(an%20HIV%20preventative%20regimen)%20or%20living%20with%20HIV%2C%20and%20who%20had%20gonorrhea%2C%20chlamydia%2C%20or%20syphilis%20within%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDoctors%20say%20anyone%20who%20has%20unprotected%20sex%20could%20benefit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20CDC%20recommendation%20focuses%20on%20high-risk%20populations%2C%20the%20science%20shows%20%26quot%3Bthat%20doxycycline%20would%20be%20effective%20regardless%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgay-lesbian-asexual-what-are-all-the-sexualities%5C%22%3Egender%20identity%20or%20sexual%20preference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr.%20Dahlia%20Philips%2C%20an%20infectious%20disease%20physician%20and%20medical%20director%20for%20Partnership%20in%20Care%20at%20MetroPlusHealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fmedia%2Freleases%2F2023%2Fs0411-sti.html%5C%22%3E2.5%20million%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20syphilis%2C%20gonorrhea%2C%20and%20chlamydia%20were%20recorded%20in%20the%20US%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20looking%20at%20how%20doxy-PEP%20reduces%20STIs%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fcisgender%5C%22%3Ecisgender%3C%2Fa%3E%20women%20and%20cisgender%20heterosexual%20men%20is%20ongoing%2C%20Purdy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%2C%20Purdy%20emphasized%20anyone%20can%20talk%20to%20their%20doctor%20today%20about%20using%20doxycycline%20to%20prevent%20STIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20medication%20is%20already%20approved%20for%20use%20in%20anyone%2012%20or%20older%2C%20and%20an%20updated%20CDC%20recommendation%20isn't%20necessary%20for%20doctors%20to%20prescribe%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECondoms%20are%20still%20important%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CDC%20recommendation%20is%20in%20what's%20called%20a%20public%20comment%20period%2C%20which%20will%20last%20through%20mid-November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20gives%20doctors%2C%20healthcare%20providers%2C%20and%20the%20public%20the%20chance%20to%20recommend%20what%20should%20be%20included%20in%20the%20CDC%20guidelines%20and%20explain%20what%20their%20experience%20has%20been%20if%20they're%20already%20prescribing%20doxy-PEP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20if%20the%20CDC%20adopts%20the%20recommendation%2C%20it%20could%20help%20increase%20doxy-PEP%20use%2C%20since%20many%20healthcare%20providers%20and%20patients%20follow%20CDC%20guidelines%20to%20understand%20best%20practices%20in%20health%2C%20ranging%20from%20COVID%20quarantine%20times%20to%20how%20to%20responsibly%20prescribe%20opioids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWidespread%20access%20to%20medical%20options%20to%20reduce%20STIs%2C%20like%20doxy-PEP%20and%20PrEP%2C%20are%20important%2C%20Philips%20said.%20But%20they're%20only%20one%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sexual%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegular%20STI%20tests%20and%20the%20use%20of%20barriers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fhow-to-put-on-a-condom%5C%22%3Econdoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bmust%20not%20be%20forgotten%20and%20should%20also%20be%20a%20part%20of%20sexual%20health%20discussions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F