0was%20a%20lot%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%20Buffett%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT6HHwOoq9M4%26t%3D5s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esat%20down%20with%20host%20George%20Goodman%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20PBS%20show%20%26quot%3BAdam%20Smith's%20Money%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20what%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20Buffett's%20first-ever%20national%20TV%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20striking%20is%20how%20consistent%20Buffett's%20views%20towards%20investing%20have%20been%20nearly%2040%20years%20later.%20These%20are%20the%20best%20pieces%20of%20investment%20wisdom%20he%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E1.%20Number%20one%20rule%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20rule%20of%20an%20investment%20is%20don't%20lose.%20And%20the%20second%20rule%20of%20investment%20is%20don't%20forget%20the%20first%20rule.%20And%20that's%20all%20the%20rules%20there%20are.%20If%20you%20buy%20things%20for%20far%20below%20what%20they're%20worth%2C%20and%20you%20buy%20a%20group%20of%20them%2C%20you%20basically%20don't%20lose%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E2.%20Most%20important%20quality%20for%20investment%20manager%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20temperamental%20quality%2C%20not%20an%20intellectual%20quality.%20You%20don't%20need%20tons%20of%20IQ%20in%20this%20business.%20I%20mean%2C%20you%20have%20to%20have%20enough%20IQ%20to%20get%20from%20here%20to%20downtown%20Omaha%2C%20but%20you%20do%20not%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20play%20three-dimensional%20chess%20or%20be%20in%20the%20top%20leagues%20in%20terms%20of%20bridge%20playing%20or%20something%20of%20the%20sort.%20You%20need%20a%20stable%20personality.%20You%20need%20a%20temperament%20that%20neither%20derives%20great%20pleasure%20from%20being%20with%20the%20crowd%20or%20against%20the%20crowd%20because%20this%20is%20not%20a%20business%20where%20you%20take%20polls.%20It's%20a%20business%20where%20you%20think.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E3.%20What%20most%20investors%20get%20wrong%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20not%20really%20think%20of%20themselves%20as%20owning%20a%20piece%20of%20a%20business.%20The%20real%20test%20of%20whether%20you're%20investing%20from%20a%20value%20standpoint%20or%20not%20is%20whether%20you%20care%20whether%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20open%20tomorrow.%20If%20you're%20making%20a%20good%20investment%20in%20a%20security%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20bother%20if%20they%20closed%20down%20the%20stock%20market%20for%20five%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E4.%20On%20checking%20stock%20prices%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20ticker%20tells%20me%20is%20the%20price.%20And%20I%20can%20look%20at%20the%20price%20occasionally%20to%20see%20whether%20the%20price%20is%20outlandishly%20cheap%20or%20outlandishly%20high%20but%20prices%20don't%20tell%20me%20anything%20about%20a%20business.%20Business%20figures%20themselves%20tell%20me%20something%20about%20a%20business%2C%20but%20the%20price%20of%20a%20stock%20doesn't%20tell%20me%20anything%20about%20a%20business.%20I%20would%20rather%20value%20a%20stock%20or%20a%20business%20first%2C%20and%20not%20even%20know%20the%20price%2C%20so%20that%20I'm%20not%20influenced%20by%20the%20price%20in%20establishing%20my%20valuation%20and%20then%20look%20at%20the%20price%20later%20to%20see%20whether%20it's%20way%20out%20of%20line%20with%20what%20my%20value%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E5.%20Omaha%20versus%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENebraska%3A%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20we%20get%20mail%20here%20and%20we%20get%20periodicals%20and%20we%20get%20all%20the%20facts%20needed%20to%20make%20decisions.%20And%20unlike%20Wall%20Street%2C%20you'll%20notice%20we%20don't%20have%2050%20people%20coming%20up%20and%20whispering%20in%20our%20ear%20that%20we%20should%20be%20doing%20this%20or%20that%20this%20afternoon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20on%20Wall%20Street%20I'd%20probably%20be%20a%20lot%20poorer.%20You%20get%20overstimulated%20on%20Wall%20Street.%20And%20you%20hear%20lots%20of%20things%2C%20and%20you%20may%20shorten%20your%20focus%20and%20a%20short%20focus%20is%20not%20conducive%20to%20long%20profits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E6.%20Not%20owning%20technology%20stocks%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20haven't%20%5Bever%20bought%20a%20technology%20company%5D.%20I%20haven't%20understood%20any%20of%20them.%20Never%20owned%20IBM.%20Marvelous%20company%2C%20I%20mean%20a%20sensational%20company%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20owned%20IBM.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E7.%20Missing%20market%20trends%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20to%20make%20money%20in%20every%20game.%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20cocoa%20beans%20are%20gonna%20do.%20There%20are%20all%20kinds%20of%20things%20I%20don't%20know%20about%2C%20and%20that%20may%20be%20too%20bad.%20But%20you%20know%2C%20why%20should%20I%20know%20all%20about%20it%3F%20I%20haven't%20worked%20that%20hard%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E8.%20Waiting%20for%20the%20right%20pitch%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20called%20strikes%20in%20the%20business.%20The%20pitcher%20just%20stands%20there%20and%20throws%20balls%20at%20you...%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20swing%20at%20any%20of%20them.%20They%20may%20be%20wonderful%20pitches%20to%20swing%20at%2C%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20know%20enough%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20swing.%20And%20you%20can%20sit%20there%20and%20watch%20thousands%20of%20pitches%20and%20finally%20get%20one%20right%20there%20where%20you%20wanted%20something%20that%20you%20understand%2C%20and%20then%20you%20swing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E9.%20Market%20timing%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20being%20asked%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20business%20opportunity%2C%20would%20it%20make%20any%20difference%20to%20me%20whether%20I%20bought%20it%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20or%20a%20Saturday%20or%20an%20election%20year%20or%20something%3F%20It's%20not%20what%20a%20businessman%20thinks%20about%20in%20buying%20businesses.%20So%20why%20think%20about%20it%20when%20buying%20stocks%3F%20Because%20stocks%20are%20just%20pieces%20of%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-stock-market-investing-wisdom-top-rules-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697892301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532d1c096f7540cd0621128%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-stock-market-investing-wisdom-top-rules-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett%20was%20worth%20%24500%20million%20when%20he%20sat%20down%20with%20for%20his%20first-ever%20national%20TV%20interview%20with%20PBS%20in%201985.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-stock-market-investing-wisdom-top-rules-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20warship%20was%20locked%20in%209-hour%20battle%20near%20Yemen%20coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697892005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104610832%2Cimgsize-85088.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-warship-was-locked-in-9-hour-battle-near-yemen-coast%2Farticleshow%2F104610822.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20warship%20intercepted%20and%20shot%20down%204%20cruise%20missiles%20and%2015%20drones%20near%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen.%20The%20missiles%20were%20fired%20by%20Houthi%20forces%20in%20Yemen%20with%20support%20from%20Iran%2C%20potentially%20targeting%20Israel.%20The%20USS%20Carney%20used%20SM-2%20surface-to-air%20missiles%20to%20intercept%20the