de%20the%20switch%20to%20entrepreneurship.%20Here's%20how%20I%20got%20my%20MBA%20from%20the%20NBA.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Baron%20Davis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532989096908fd7cdb3ba8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20Hodgin%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EBaron%20Davis%20is%20a%20former%20NBA%20player%20who's%20making%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20off%20the%20court%20in%20the%20business%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHis%20latest%20venture%2C%20Business%20In%20the%20Game%2C%20is%20a%20platform%20for%20athletes%20and%20talent%20looking%20to%20become%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EDavis%20spoke%20with%20Insider%20reporter%20Yoonji%20Han%20about%20his%20transition%20from%20the%20NBA%20to%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20former%20NBA%20player%20and%20entrepreneur%20Baron%20Davis.%20The%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%203%20years%20old%2C%20my%20grandfather%20built%20a%20basketball%20court%20for%20me%20for%20Christmas.%20That%20initiated%20my%20love%20for%20basketball.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20court%20he'd%20built%20in%20his%20backyard%2C%20it%20was%20just%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20do%20this%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20the%20one%20thing%20he%20knew%20I%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20it%20was%20every%20day%2C%20all%20day%2C%20basketball%2C%20basketball%2C%20basketball.%20I%20started%20learning%20to%20shoot%20the%20ball%20at%20nine%20or%2010%20feet%20because%20my%20older%20cousins%20would%20come%20and%20raise%20the%20hoop%20up.%20But%20my%20grandmother%20would%20water%20around%20the%20basket%20at%20night%2C%20and%20the%20court%2C%20which%20was%20built%20on%20dirt%2C%20would%20sink%20back%20down%20so%20I%20could%20make%20shots%20as%20a%20little%20kid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasketball%20has%20been%20the%20instrument%20to%20the%20story%20of%20my%20life.%20It%20was%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20kept%20me%20grounded%20through%20the%20ups%20and%20down.%20It%20also%20allowed%20me%20to%20move%20across%20the%20city%3A%20I%20got%20a%20scholarship%20to%20a%20private%20school%2C%20which%20formed%20my%20perspective%20of%20what%20the%20real%20world%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20to%20Santa%20Monica%20every%20day%20and%20then%20coming%20home%20to%20South%20Central%2C%20there%20was%20always%20this%20reality%20check%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20there's%20this%20world%20out%20there%20that%20exists%2C%20but%20also%20this%20world%20does%20not%20exist%20for%20people%20like%20you.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20in%20survival%20mode%20all%20the%20time%2C%20looking%20for%20mentors%20and%20guides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20NBA%20journey%20on%20and%20off%20the%20court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wound%20up%20at%20UCLA%2C%20and%20my%20mission%20was%20always%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20build%20that%20bridge%20where%20kids%20in%20my%20neighborhood%20can%20wake%20up%20and%20have%20the%20same%20experience%20as%20the%20kids%20going%20to%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20NBA%20career%2C%20it's%20always%20been%20about%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20I%20become%20a%20beacon%20of%20light%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20hopefully%20someone's%20watching%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYo%2C%20if%20Baron%20Davis%20did%20it%2C%20I%20can%20do%20it%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fknicks-point-guards-2010-where-are-they-now-2020-12%5C%22%3Ethe%20career%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20have%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Once%20I%20turned%20pro%2C%20I%20was%20injured%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20because%20basketball%20was%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20really%20had%2C%20I%20played%20injured%20a%20lot.%20I%20never%20g