ts%20you%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20rooms%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20can't%20get%20in.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20realized%20there's%20an%20order%20and%20a%20process%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20learn%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20my%20MBA%20from%20the%20NBA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20the%20only%20athlete%20for%20a%20long%20time%20at%20these%20venture%20conferences%2C%20I%20heard%20people%20speak%20negatively%20about%20athletes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0about%20their%20money%2C%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-af-modeling-itself-after-whole-foods-valued-200-million-2021-12%5C%22%3Einvestments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20what%20they're%20doing.%20The%20overall%20zeitgeist%20was%20this%20narrative%20that%20athletes%20are%20dumb%20and%20are%20going%20to%20go%20broke%2C%20and%20they%20need%20people%20like%20us%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%20with%20their%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20needed%20to%20go%20and%20find%20great%20athletes%20doing%20dope%20stuff%2C%20that%20are%20doing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funest-pitch-deck-series-a-fintech-2020-6%5C%22%3Egreat%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20creating%20incredible%20businesses%2C%20and%20branding%20themselves%20as%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bigsummit.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Inside%20the%20Game%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20realized%20that%20it's%20time%20to%20start%20showing%20people%20that%20we%20exist%20in%20this%20space.%20And%20it%20can't%20just%20be%20athletes%20and%20entertainers.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20the%20investors%2C%20the%20C-suites%2C%20the%20connectors%2C%20the%20media%2C%20because%20we%20all%20play%20a%20part%20in%20the%20trajectory%20of%20a%20company%20becoming%20a%20unicorn%20or%20having%20an%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3