0being%20photographed.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532d821be9edfa8eda67835%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Bankman%20Fried%20leaves%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%20following%20a%20pre-trial%20hearing.%3Cp%3ECraig%20Ruttle%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20high%20bar%20to%20clear%2C%20according%20to%20Sarah%20Krissoff%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20Cozen%20O'Connor%20and%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%20in%20New%20York.%20But%20Bankman-Fried's%20attorneys%20may%20convince%20jurors%20that%20Bankman-Fried%20genuinely%20believed%20his%20actions%20were%20acceptable%20in%20the%20wild-west%20cryptocurrency%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20thought%20this%20was%20okay%20in%20this%20world%20where%20crypto%20wasn't%20regulated%2C%20and%20so%20he%20had%20sort%20of%20no%20concept%20that%20this%20was%20a%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20Krissoff%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20if%20all%20of%20the%20other%20insider%20witnesses%20have%20said%2C%20'I%20knew%20this%20was%20wrong%2C%20and%20I%20pled%20guilty%20to%20crimes%20related%20to%20it.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%2C%20Singh%2C%20and%20Wang%20were%20all%20in%20Bankman-Fried's%20inner%20circle.%20Ellison%20led%20Alameda%20Research%20for%20much%20of%202021%20and%202022.%20Wang%20co-founded%20Alameda%20and%20FTX%20with%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20led%20the%20latter%20as%20its%20chief%20technology%20officer.%20Singh%20knew%20Bankman-Fried%20since%20he%20was%20in%20high%20school%20and%20was%20the%20top%20developer%20at%20FTX%2C%20having%20intimate%20knowledge%20of%20its%20code.%20All%20of%20them%20lived%20together%20in%20a%20%2435%20million%20penthouse%20that%20Bankman-Fried%20purchased%20in%20the%20Bahamas%20with%20Alameda's%20funds.%20And%20all%20of%20them%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20conspiring%20with%20Bankman-Fried%20to%20take%20customer%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20for%20Bankman-Fried's%20attorneys%20is%20to%20convince%20jurors%20that%20he%20didn't%20know%20about%20any%20wrongdoing.%20They've%20suggested%20that%20Bankman-Fried's%20former%20lieutenants%20and%20close%20friends%20are%20motivated%20to%20testify%20against%20him%20in%20hopes%20of%20getting%20lighter%20sentences%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20question%20isn't%20so%20much%20necessarily%2C%20'Is%20all%20of%20that%20wrong%2C%20or%20is%20that%20stuff%20criminal%3F'%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Tuchmann%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20Wiggin%20and%20Dana%2C%20and%20a%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%20in%20New%20York.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20'Did%20SBF%20know%20about%20it%3F%20Did%20he%20direct%20them%20to%20do%20it%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEveryone%20has%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20SBF%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20defense%20attorneys%20have%20tried%20to%20obfuscate%20each%20witnesses'%20relationship%20with%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20his%20knowledge%20of%20wrongdoing%2C%20those%20witnesses%20have%20been%20forthright%20on%20the%20witness%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20flipped%20everybody%20else%20in%20order%20to%20prosecute%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%2C%26quot%3B%20Krissoff%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20doing%20that%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20multiple%20other%20individuals%20have%20agreed%20'I%20knew%20I%20was%20doing%20something%20wrong%2C%20I%20was%20committing%20a%20crime%2C%20I%20did%20something%20wrong%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20illegal%20at%20the%20time'%20%E2%80%94%20it%20doesn't%20help%20his%20intent%20argument.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20does%20have%20some%20points%20in%20his%20favor.%20In%20one%20memo%20shown%20to%20jurors%2C%20circulated%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202022%20%E2%80%94%20before%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20collapsed%20%E2%80%94%20Bankman-Fried%20lamented%20Ellison's%20skills%20running%20Alameda%20while%20he%20focused%20on%20FTX.%20He%20said%20the%20trading%20firm%20would%20have%20done%20better%20if%20he%20were%