od.%20Their%20son%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20pursued%20music%20under%20the%20stage%20name%20Henry%20Wolfe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20have%20five%20grandchildren%20together%20as%20well.%20Their%20son%20has%20two%20children%20with%20his%20wife%20Tomaryn%20Storm%20Hawker.%20Their%20daughter%2C%20Mamie%20Gummer%2C%20has%20two%20children%20with%20her%20husband%20Mehar%20Sethi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20work%20front%2C%20Meryl%20Streep%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20season%20three%20of%20%3Cem%3E'Only%20Murders%20In%20The%20Building'.%3C%2Fem%3E%20According%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnbcmiami.com%2Fentertainment%2Fentertainment-news%2Fmeryl-streep-and-husband-don-gummer-announce-split-after-45-years-of-marriage%2F3139068%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20NBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20most%20Oscar%20nominations%20of%20any%20actor%20with%2021%2C%20including%20for%20her%20roles%20in%3Cem%3E%20'The%20Post%2C%20'Into%20the%20Woods'%2C%20'The%20Iron%20Lady'%2C%20'The%20Devil%20Wears%20Prada'%2C%20'Out%20of%20Africa'%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3E'Kramer%20vs%20Kramer'.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fov5v6pp8_meryl-streep_625x300_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meryl%20Street%20and%20her%20husband%20of%2045%20years%2C%20Don%20Gummer%2C%20have%20been%20secretly%20separated%20for%20over%20six%20years%2C%20Page%20Six%20reported%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manual%20Scavenging%3A%20SC%20Hikes%20Compensation%20to%20Rs%2030%20Lakh%2C%20Orders%20Govt%20to%20Ensure%20Complete%20Ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F06191314%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-06-at-7.12.59-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20directing%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20ensure%20the%20complete%20eradication%20of%20manual%20scavenging%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2020%2C%20ordered%20the%20compensation%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20sewer%20deaths%20to%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20compensation%20amount%20in%20the%20case%20of%20permanent%20disability%20be%20made%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20be%20given%20for%20other%20forms%20of%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20S.%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20and%20Justice%20Aravind%20Kumar%20issued%2014%20directions%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20Act%2C%202013.%20The%20orders%20also%20called%20for%20proper%20rehabilitation%20measures%20for%20victims%20and%20their%20families%2C%20including%20the%20disbursement%20of%20scholarships%20and%20the%20availability%20of%20skill%20development%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fsupreme-court%2Fcompletely-eradicate-manual-scavenging-supreme-court-directs-union-states-increases-compensation-for-sewer-deaths-to-rs-30-lakh-240650%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20court%2C%20passing%20its%20verdict%20in%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20against%20the%20employment%20of%20manual%20scavengers%2C%20said%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CUnion%20and%20States%20are%20duty-bound%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20practice%20of%20manual%20scavenging%20is%20completely%20eradicated.%20Each%20of%20us%20owes%20to%20this%20large%20segment%20of%20the%20population%20who%20have%20remained%20unseen%2C%20unheard%2C%20and%20muted%2C%20in%20bondage%20systematically%20trapped%20in%20inhuman%20conditions.%20The%20conferment%20of%20entitlements%20and%20placement%20of%20obligations%20upon%20the%20Union%20and%20States%20through%20the%20express%20prohibitions%20in%20the%20constitution%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%202013%20Act%20means%20that%20they%20are%20obliged%20to%20implement%20the%20provisions%20in%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20went%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20without%20reason%20that%20our%20constitution%20has%20placed%20great%20emphasis%20on%20the%20value%20of%20dignity%20and%20fraternity.%20But%20for%20these%20two%2C%20all%20other%20liberties%20are%20a%20chimera.%20All%20of%20us%20today%20who%20proudly%20bask%20in%20the%20achievements%20of%20our%20republic%20have%20to%20awake%20and%20arise%20so%20that%20the%20darkness%20which%20has%20been%20the%20fate%20of%20generations%20of%20our%20people%20is%20dispelled%20and%20they%20enjoy%20these%20freedoms%20and%20justice-%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20take%20for%20granted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20be%20next%20heard%20on%20February%201%2C%202024%2C%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F339-lives-lost-to-manual-scavenging-in-the-last-five-years-govt-data-reveals%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Union%20social%20justice%20and%20empowerment%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20339%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20while%20cleaning%20sewers%20and%20septic%20tanks%20in%20India%20between%202018%20and%202023.%20As%20per%20the%20data%20presented%20before%20the%20parliament%20by%20the%20government%2C%C2%A0nine%20such%20deaths%20were%20recorded%20in%202023%2C%2066%20in%202022%2C%2058%20in%202021%2C%2022%20in%202020%2C%20117%20in%202019%2C%20and%2067%20deaths%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManual%20scavenging%20is%20an%20outlawed%20practice%20under%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20(PEMSR)%20Act%2C%202013.%20The%20Act%20bans%20the%20use%20of%20any%20individual%20for%20manually%20cleaning%2C%20carrying%2C%20disposing%20of%2C%20or%20otherwise%20handling%2C%20in%20any%20manner%2C%20human%20excreta%20till%20its%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889625000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F06191314%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-06-at-7.12.59-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanual-scavenging-sc-hikes-compensation-to-rs-30-lakh-orders-govt-to-ensure-complete-ban%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20S.%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20and%20Justice%20Aravind%20Kumar%20issued%2014%20directions%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20Act%2C%202013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanual-scavenging-sc-hikes-compensation-to-rs-30-lakh-orders-govt-to-ensure-complete-ban%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Workers%20Are%20Striking%20In%20Numbers%20Not%20Seen%20In%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22But%20any%20talk%20of%20a%20strike%20resurgence%20needs%20to%20be%20put%20in%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20a%20major%20long-term%20decline.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%