2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Taylor%20Swift%20announced%20that%20her%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-helped-us-economy-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EEras%20Tour%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20film%20would%20be%20opening%20a%20day%20early%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20were%20in%20this%20mad%20rush%20to%20get%20everything%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20Shane%2C%20a%20manager%20of%20a%20small-town%20movie%20theater%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Northwest%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20good%20that%20we%20did%20get%20people%20in%20the%20theater%20and%20I%20guess%20made%20sure%20everything%20worked%20all%20the%20way%20through.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20we%20would've%20done%20if%20it%20was%20a%20250-person%20sellout%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Insider%20verified%20his%20full%20name%20and%20employment%2C%20but%20withheld%20them%20over%20privacy%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20crowd%20wasn't%20too%20much%20to%20handle%2C%20the%20sound%20was%3A%20The%20movie%20was%20so%20loud%20that%20it's%20blown%20out%20two%20amplifiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20time%20we%20did%20a%20test%20play%2C%20one%20of%20our%20amplifiers%20blew%20up%20and%20killed%20a%20theater%2C%20which%20is%20wonderful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20On%20Sunday%20night%2C%20another%20one%20blew%20out.%20Neither%20have%20been%20able%20to%20be%20replaced%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20instructed%20to%20turn%20it%20up%20fairly%20loud.%20They%20said%20they%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20a%20true%20concert%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift's%20Eras%20Tour%20film%20is%20already%20record-smashing%2C%20bringing%20in%20between%20%2495%20and%20%2497%20million%20and%20marking%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-box-office-records-beyonce-barbie-oppenheimer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebiggest-ever%20op