disappointing%20that%20it%20was%20smaller%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20compared%20to%20all%20of%20the%20kids%20movies%20and%20horror%20movies%20that%20are%20out%20right%20now%2C%20the%20Taylor%20Swift%20fans%20are%20not%20bad%20at%20all.%20They%20don't%20really%20leave%20that%20big%20of%20a%20mess%20other%20than%2C%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20the%20occasional%20spilled%20drink%20or%20the%20occasional%20little%20spill%20of%20popcorn%2C%26quot%3B%20Shane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20kids%20movies%2C%20he%20said%2C%20you%20%26quot%3Bfind%20tons%20of%20popcorn%20everywhere%2C%20tons%20of%20candy%20everywhere%2C%20four%20or%20five%20spilled%20drinks%20in%20a%20theater.%26quot%3B%20After%20an%20Eras%20Tour%20screening%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20really%20find%20anything%20too%20awful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20he%20wants%20Eras%20Tour%20theatergoers%20to%20know%20that%20even%20if%20they've%20purchased%20tickets%20online%2C%20they'll%20still%20need%20to%20be%20scanned.%20That's%20been%20a%20friction%20point%20for%20all%20movie%20goers%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20I%20hope%20this%20concert%20style%20film%20doesn't%20become%20super%20popular%20%E2%80%94%20because%20amps%20aren't%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-movie-movie-theater-worker-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652eee46211def8ed8379a55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-movie-movie-theater-worker-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taylor%20Swift's%20Eras%20Tour%20film%20was%20so%20loud%20it%20blew%20the%20sound%20system%20in%20one%20theater.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement