assy%2Famp_articleshow%2F104609708.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMahua%20Moitra%20Mortgaged%20Country's%20Security%20For%20Money%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahua%20Moitra-Darshan%20Hiranandani%20affidavit%20controversy%20escalated%20on%20Saturday%20with%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20firing%20salvos%20at%20each%20other.%20While%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20of%20the%20BJP%20alleged%20the%20TMC%20MP%20had%20mortgaged%20the%20country's%20security%20for%20money%2C%20claiming%20that%20her%20parliamentary%20ID%20was%20used%20in%20Dubai%20when%20she%20was%20in%20India%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20hit%20back%20and%20accused%20the%20MP%20of%20leaking%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20the%20complaint%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20taking%20bribes%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20Parliament%2C%20alleged%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20National%20Informatics%20Centre%20(NIC)%20has%20informed%20an%20investigating%20agency%20that%20her%20ID%20was%20used%20in%20Dubai%20when%20she%20was%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20MP%20mortgaged%20the%20country's%20security%20for%20some%20money.%20The%20parliament%20ID%20was%20opened%20in%20Dubai%20when%20the%20so-called%20MP%20was%20in%20India.%20The%20entire%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20finance%20department%2C%20the%20central%20agencies%20are%20on%20this%20NIC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20%40AITCofficial%20and%20the%20opposition%20still%20want%20to%20do%20politics%3F%20It%20is%20the%20public's%20decision.%20NIC%20has%20given%20this%20information%20to%20the%20investigating%20agency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20without%20taking%20Ms%20Moitra's%20name%20or%20disclosing%20which%20agency%20the%20information%20had%20been%20given%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECountering%20Mr%20Dubey's%20claims%2C%20the%20TMC%20MP%20asked%20the%20NIC%20to%20release%20details%20publicly%20and%20show%20that%20MPs%20were%20physically%20present%20in%20places%20from%20where%20their%20IDs%20were%20accessed%20by%20their%20personal%20assistants%2C%20researchers%2C%20interns%20and%20staff%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20affidavit%2C%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20had%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20given%20him%20her%20parliament%20login%20ID%20to%20frame%20questions%20on%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20which%20she%20felt%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20target%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20businessman%20claimed%20Ms%20Moitra%20wanted%20to%20quickly%20make%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20at%20the%20national%20level%20and%20she%20was%20told%20by%20her%20friends%20and%20advisors%20that%20the%20shortest%20possible%20route%20to%20fame%20was%20by%20personally%20attacking%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20TMC%20MP%20made%20frequent%20demands%20and%20kept%20asking%20him%20for%20various%20favours.%20This%20included%20gifting%20her%20expensive%20luxury%20items%2C%20providing%20support%20on%20the%20renovation%20of%20her%20officially%20allotted%20bungalow%20in%20Delhi%2C%20travel%20expenses%20and%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20she%20is%20ready%20to%20face%20questions%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha's%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20which%20is%20looking%20into%20Mr%20Dubey's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fddm2s7ag_mahua-moitra_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt