m%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ffresh-formal-job-creation-slows-to-5-month-low-in-august-shows-epfo-data-123102001151_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20EPFO%20payroll%20data%20helps%20to%20track%20employment%20creation%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%2C%20as%20it%20is%20mandatory%20for%20every%20new%20employee%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20provident%20fund%20under%20the%20EPFO.%20The%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20also%20uses%20EPFO%20data%20to%20analyse%20employment%20trends%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20net%20payroll%20addition%20also%20went%20up%20marginally%20by%200.8%25%20to%201.69%20million%20in%20August%20from%20July%201.68%20million.%20The%20net%20payroll%20is%20calculated%20by%20considering%20the%20number%20of%20new%20subscribers%2C%20the%20number%20of%20exits%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20old%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20net%20monthly%20payroll%20numbers%20are%20provisional%20in%20nature%20and%20are%20revised%20sharply%20the%20following%20month.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20number%20of%20new%20EPF%20subscribers%20holds%20more%20significance%20than%20net%20additions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERituparna%20Chakraborty%20of%20TeamLease%20Services%20said%20the%20momentum%20found%20in%20the%20labour%20market%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20financial%20year%2C%20which%20generally%20prepares%20a%20holistic%20view%20of%20their%20workforce%20requirement%2C%20lost%20momentum%20by%20monsoon%20time%20as%20more%20people%20took%20to%20work%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector%2C%20Business%20Standard%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChakraborty%20continued%20to%20add%20that%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20the%20momentum%20could%20be%20picked%20up%20due%20to%20expected%20demand%20in%20retail%20and%20consumption%20sectors%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20new%20formal%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%2C%20the%20unemployment%20in%20the%20country%20in%20August%20rose%20to%208.1%25%20from%207.9%25%20in%20July%20coupled%20with%20a%20situation%20where%20there%20had%20been%20increased%20labour%20force%20participation%20and%20the%20economy%20was%20not%20able%20to%20create%20jobs%20proportionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697887859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F28134446%2F3891925784_eb02c9d8e3_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fepfo-data-with-13-3-dip-in-new-monthly-subscribers-formal-job-creation-slowed-in-august%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20monthly%20subscribers%20decreased%20from%201.06%20million%20in%20July%20to%209%2C25%2C%20984%20in%20August.%20The%20EPFO%20payroll%20data%20helps%20to%20track%20employment%20creation%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%2C%20as%20it%20is%20mandatory%20for%20every%20new%20employee%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20provident%20fund%20under%20the%20EPFO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fepfo-data-with-13-3-dip-in-new-monthly-subscribers-formal-job-creation-slowed-in-august%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICICI%20Bank%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20jumps%2036%25%20to%20Rs%2010%2C261%20cr%2C%20NII%20up%2024%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697887786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F28%2Ffull%2F1695883865-6682.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ficici-bank-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-36-to-rs-10-261-cr-nii-up-24-123102100512_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20total%20income%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20rose%20to%20Rs%2040%2C697%20crore%20from%20Rs%2031