-return%2Famp_articleshow%2F104609062.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel's%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20will%20be%20way%20more%20deadly%20than%20the%20'absolute%20hell'%20US%20Marines%20experienced%20in%20Fallujah%2C%20Iraq%2C%20geopolitical%20expert%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Marines%20in%20Fallujah%20(L)%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border%20(R).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65339efbbe9edfa8eda6bb73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Marines%20in%20Fallujah%20in%202004%20(L)%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border%20on%20October%2014%2C%202023%20(R).%3Cp%3EMurad%20Sezer%2FAP%20Photo%2C%20Mostafa%20Alkharouf%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael%20has%20indicated%20it%20will%20soon%20begin%20a%20ground%20offensive%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20geopolitical%20expert%20who%20embedded%20with%20US%20Marines%20in%20Fallujah%20said%20it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20hell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20Gaza's%20dense%20population%20and%20Hamas'%20vast%20underground%20tunnels%20will%20pose%20challenges.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20anticipated%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20will%20be%20far%20more%20destructive%20and%20difficult%20than%20the%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20hell%26quot%3B%20that%20US%20Marines%20experienced%20in%20Fallujah%20in%20Iraq%2C%20a%20geopolitical%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20this%20as%20just%20absolute%20hell%20and%20magnified%20by%20many%20times%2C%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.robertdkaplan.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejournalist%20and%20author%20Robert%20D.%20Kaplan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20embedded%20with%20the%20Marines%20in%20Fallujah%20in%20April%202004%2C%20told%20the%20podcast%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehub.ca%2F2023-10-17%2Frobert-d-kaplan-on-what-israel-can-learn-from-the-absolute-hell-of-the-first-battle-of-fallujah%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHub%20Dialogues.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20what%20I%20experienced%20in%20Fallujah%20is%20that%20because%20you're%20dealing%20with%20hardened%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20well-trained%20and%20disciplined%20adversaries%2C%20this%20can't%20be%20anything%20but%20a%20mess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan%20was%20discussing%20what%20became%20known%20as%20the%20First%20Battle%20of%20Fallujah%2C%20code-named%20Operation%20Vigilant%20Resolve%2C%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20central%20Iraqi%20city%20and%20a%20hotbed%20of%20the%20insurgency%2C%20launched%20following%20the%20death%20and%20mutilation%20of%20four%20US%20contractors%20before%20their%20burned%20corpses%20were%20hung%20over%20a%20bridge%20crossing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20broadcast%20globally%20caused%20great%20anger%20in%20the%20US.Troops%20of%20the%201st%20Marine%20Division%20attempted%20to%20capture%20the%20city.%C2%A0%20After%20three%20weeks%20of%20fighting%2C%2027%20US%20servicemen%20lay%20dead%2C%20and%20an%20estimated%20600%20Iraqi%20civilians%20and%20200%20insurgents%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan%20noted%20that%20any%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20will%20also%20likely%20to%20result%20in%20huge%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaza%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20places%20in%20the%20world%2C%20with%20over%20two%20million%20people%20living%20in%20a%20strip%20spanning%20140%20square%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20Fallujah%20at%20the%20time%20was%20far%20less%20densely%20populated%20than%20Gaza%20is%20now.%20It%20had%20no%20underground%20tunnels%20or%20anything%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20nothing%20like%20apartment%20houses%20right%20next%20to%20each%20other%20which%20you%20have%20in%20Gaza%20City.%20I%20don't%20see%20how%20it%20can%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Marines'%20adversaries%20in%20Fallujah%20were%20more%20familiar%20with%20the%20urban%20terrain%2C%20and%20fire%20would%20often%20come%20from%20multiple%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Marines%20only%20targeted%20young%20men%20with%20guns%20in%20Fallujah%2C%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20avoid%20hitting%20civilians%2C%20he%20said%2C%20which%20will%20likely%20be%20the%20same%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20the%20added%20advantage%20of%20a%20well-developed%20tunnel%20network%20under%20the%20strip%2C%20which%20they%20use%20to%20smuggle%20weapons%20and%20move%20around%20undetected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20his%20experience%20in%20Fallujah%20was%20one%20of%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20hell%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%20it%20being%20on%20paper%20%26quot%3Bfar%20less%20daunting%20than%20what%20the%20Israelis%20face.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20an%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20would%20be%20far%20more%20complex%20despite%20massive%20advancements%20in%20war%20technology%20and%20Israel%20having%20more%20air%20cover%20than%20the%20Marines%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan%20said%20that%20Israeli%20forces%20must%20find%20%26quot%3Bthe%20sweet%20spot%20between%20the%20restoration%20of%20deterrence%20and%20all-out%20Stalingrad-style%20warfare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20what%20could%20be%20more%20manageable%20would%20be%20to%20avoid%20an%20all-out%20Russian-style%20invasion.%20Instead%2C%20several%20units%20could%20enter%20Gaza%20with%20targeted%20objectives%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20take%20the%20whole%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Indeed%2C%20in%20the%20Second%20Battle%20of%20Fallujah%20in%20November%20of%202004%2C%20US-led%20forces%20used%20more%20sophisticated%20tactics.%20The%20city%20was%20occupied%20after%20intense%20fighting%2C%20and%20two-thirds%20of%20its%20300%2C000%20population%20had%20fled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20have%20signaled%20that%20they%20are%20prepared%20to%20imminently%20begin%20a%20ground%20offensive%20into%20northern%20Gaza%20to%20root%20out%20Hamas%20militants%20following%20a%20deadly%20attack%20by%20the%20group%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%20attacks%20killed%20at%20least%201%2C400%20Israelis%2C%20and%20subsequent%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20have%20killed%20more%20than%203%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fleast-500-victims-israeli-air-strike-hospital-gaza-health-ministry-2023-10-17%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHealth%2520authorities%2520in%2520Gaza%2520said%2Cthan%25201%252C300%2520soldiers%2520and%2520civilians.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20also%20took%20over%20200%20hostages%20to%20Gaza%2C%20and%20it%20is%20unclear%20where%20they%20are%20being%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20northern%20Gaza%20have%20been%20fleeing%20south%20after%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20gave%20an%20evacuation%20order%2C%20resulting%20in%20one%20million%20people%20being%20internally%20displaced%2C%20per%20UN%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20called%20up%20some%20360%2C000%20reservists%20following%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20and%20officials%20have%20indicated%20that%20the%20offensive%20will%20begin%20soon%20and%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Ftop-officials-say-gaza-ground-offensive-soon-warn-it-will-be-long-and-intense%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Blong%20and%20intense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraels-gaza-offensive-much-harder-us-marines-fallujah-battle-expert-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697887462000%2