the%20enemy.%20From%20110%20youth%20who%20joined%20militancy%20last%20year%2C%20only%2010%20have%20joined%20militancy%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dilbag%20Singh%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20out%20of%2010%20local%20terrorists%2C%20six%20have%20already%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20even%20these%2010%20had%20not%20gone%20to%20the%20other%20side.%20It%20would%20been%20so%20nice%20and%20we%20would%20have%20told%20the%20world%20that%20all%20the%20youth%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20are%20on%20the%20side%20of%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20chief%20said%20that%20four%20other%20local%20men%20moving%20around%20with%20weapons%20may%20also%20be%20killed%20in%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20asked%20the%20four%20suspected%20terrorists%20to%20surrender%2C%20adding%20the%20doors%20of%20%26quot%3Bghar%20wapsi%26quot%3B%20are%20open%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dramatic%20drop%20in%20recruitment%20of%20local%20men%20in%20terrorist%20ranks%20is%20the%20biggest%20achievement%20after%20three%20decades%20of%20fight%20against%20militancy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20best%20security%20scenario%20Kashmir%20had%20witnessed%20was%20in%202013%20when%20total%20number%20of%20terrorists%20had%20come%20down%20to%20a%20few%20dozen%20and%20casualties%20of%20civilians%20and%20security%20forces%20was%20at%20an%20all-time%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20changed%20after%202014%20and%20recruitment%20of%20locals%20joining%20terrorist%20ranks%20was%20increasing%20by%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Article%20370%20was%20scrapped%20in%202019%2C%20a%20massive%20crackdown%20was%20launched%20against%20separatists%20and%20their%20support%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20demolished%20separatist%20structure%2C%20recruitment%20of%20locals%20as%20terrorists%20remained%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20119%20locals%20joined%20terrorism%20in%20Kashmir.%20In%202020%20the%20number%20jumped%20to%20167.%20It%20was%20128%20in%202021%20and%20110%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20number%20of%20security%20forces%20deployed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20surpassed%20all%20the%20previous%20records.%20It%20has%20ensured%20end%20of%20stone%20throwing%20and%20pro-separatist%20protests%20and%20shutdowns%20in%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20stringent%20security%20measures%20within%20the%20Valley%2C%20killing%20of%20several%20terrorist%20commanders%20in%20targeted%20attacks%20inside%20Pakistan%20appears%20to%20have%20delivered%20a%20huge%20blow%20to%20terrorist%20organizations%20and%20their%20capacity%20to%20recruit%20and%20arm%20local%20youth%20in%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697886600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fd4qb2atg_dilbag-singh-1200_625x300_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorism-on-its-last-leg-in-jammu-and-kashmir-what-top-cop-said-4502620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Only%2010%20local%20recruits%20have%20joined%20the%20terrorist%20ranks%20this%20year%2C%20said%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20today%2C%20adding%20that%20six%20of%20them%20have%20already%20been%20killed%2C%20while%20four%20others%20have%20the%20option%20to%20surrender%20or%20get%20killed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorism-on-its-last-leg-in-jammu-and-kashmir-what-top-cop-said-4502620%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorism-on-its-last-leg-in-jammu-and-kashmir-what-top-cop-said-4502620%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorism-on-its-last-leg-in-jammu-and-kashmir-what-top-cop-said-4502620%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C