%20that%20several%20students%20had%20left%20seats%20in%20others%20streams%20to%20join%20the%20MBBS%20course%20and%20would%20now%20be%20staring%20at%20losing%20an%20academic%20year.%20The%20report%20said%20while%20more%20than%20600%20students%20are%20likely%20to%20lose%20their%20admission%20for%20violation%20of%20the%20NMC%20guidelines%20by%20the%20institutes%2C%20mismanagement%20of%20the%20counselling%20process%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20result%20in%20more%20than%202000%20MBBS%20seats%20across%20the%20country%20going%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NMC%20had%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fedugraph%2Fnews%2Fnmc-issues-warning-mbbs-admissions-post-september-30-deemed-invalid%2Fcid%2F1974639%5C%22%3Eissued%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20deadline%20of%20October%2020%2C%202023%2C%20for%20all%20medical%20colleges%20to%20provide%20details%20of%20the%20first-year%20MBBS%20admissions%20for%20the%202023-24%20academic%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697885906000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21162624%2F2-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fnational-medical-commission-mbbs-students-deadline%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20notification%20issued%20by%20Shambhu%20Sharan%20Kumar%2C%20director%20of%20undergraduate%20medical%20education%20board%2C%20said%20the%20admissions%20of%20those%20who%20were%20accommodated%20after%20the%20September%2030%20deadline%20would%20be%20declared%20'invalid.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fnational-medical-commission-mbbs-students-deadline%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uncertainty%20for%20600%20MBBS%20Students%20As%20NMC%20Asks%20to%20Discharge%20Those%20Admitted%20After%20Deadline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-con