84680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F9mgupkm_harbhajan-singh-youtube_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbring-mohammed-shami-in-his-place-harbhajan-singh-wants-this-india-star-to-be-dropped-vs-new-zealand-4501927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Team%20India%20suffered%20a%20major%20blow%20during%20their%20previous%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20as%20their%20vice-captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%20picked%20up%20an%20ankle%20injury%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbring-mohammed-shami-in-his-place-harbhajan-singh-wants-this-india-star-to-be-dropped-vs-new-zealand-4501927%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbring-mohammed-shami-in-his-place-harbhajan-singh-wants-this-india-star-to-be-dropped-vs-new-zealand-4501927%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbring-mohammed-shami-in-his-place-harbhajan-singh-wants-this-india-star-to-be-dropped-vs-new-zealand-4501927%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20the%20%E2%80%98Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%E2%80%99%20Pandal%20Cannot%20Be%20a%20Centrepiece%20of%20Kolkata's%20Durga%20Puja%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161334%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Durga%20Puja%20in%20Kolkata%20is%20known%20for%20its%20syncretism.%20Here%2C%20celebrations%20cross%20religious%20and%20communal%20boundaries%2C%20and%20people%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religions%2C%20visit%20the%20puja%20pandals%20(decorated%20pavilions)%20dotting%20the%20city%2C%20something%20which%20we%2C%20the%20natives%20of%20the%20city%2C%20are%20proud%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20these%20times%20of%20commercialisation%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20many%20of%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Ctheme%E2%80%9D%20pujas%20focus%20on%20themes%20of%20communal%20harmony%20and%20other%20socially%20progressive%20topics.%20In%20the%20background%20of%20this%20inter-communal%20amity%2C%20the%20replica%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20being%20celebrated%20as%20a%20major%20puja%20destination%20in%20central%20Kolkata%20hits%20a%20highly%20dissonant%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20puja%20pandal%2C%20lit%20by%20psychedelic%20lights%20and%20lasers%2C%20has%20apparently%20been%20drawing%20record%20crowds%20from%20even%20before%20the%20pujas%20formally%20began%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20October%2020.%20The%20puja%20is%20organised%20by%20Sajal%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20councillor%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(who%20is%20also%20the%20son%20of%20an%20ex-Congress%20leader%20who%20was%20the%20original%20organiser%20of%20the%20puja).%20Union%20home%20minister%20and%20BJP%20bigwig%20Amit%20Shah%20especially%20flew%20in%20from%20Delhi%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20pandal%20on%20October%2016.%20In%20his%20speech%20during%20the%20inauguration%2C%20he%20specifically%20mentioned%20that%20the%20puja%20pandal%20was%20a%20preview%20of%20the%20actual%20Ram%20temple%20coming%20up%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Since%20then%2C%20along%20with%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20a%20long%20lineup%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20including%20the%20Union%20education%20minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20and%20MP%20and%20head%20of%20the%20BJP%20youth%20wing%20Tejaswi%20Surya%20have%20visited%20the%20pandal.%20So%20have%20the%20governor%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20high%20court%2C%20Justice%20T.S.%20Sivagnanam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20ostensible%20popularity%20and%20celebrity%20visits%2C%20what%20is%20lost%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20pandal%20celebrates%20a%20religious%20place%20that%20is%20being%20established%20upon%20the%20destruction%20of%20another%20place%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fayodhyatimeline%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Babri%2520Masjid%2520is%2520constructed%2Cwas%2520the%2520birthplace%2520of%2520Rama.%5C%22%3EAyodhya%3A%20Once%20There%20Was%20A%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EForgotten%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20final%20construction%20of%20this%20temple%20is%20a%20culmination%20of%20a%20process%20marked%20by%20many%20years%20of%20communal%20discord%2C%20riots%2C%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20the%20misery%20of%20people%20of%20both%20communities%20of%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20That%20it%20finally%20marks%20the%20subjugation%20and%20disrespect%20of%20a%20religious%20community%20in%20a%20country%20constitutionally%20declared%20to%20be%20secular%20and%20democratic.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-ayodhya-verdict-possession%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520The%2520Supreme%2520Court%2527s%2Cwas%2520offered%2520in%2520the%2520mosque%5C%22%3Ein%20its%20verdict%20in%20November%202019%20handed%20over%20the%20disputed%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20which%20the%20mosque%20once%20stood%20to%20the%20Hindu%20side%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20temple.%20The%20court%20also%20ordered%20that%20a%20trust%20be%20formed%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20which%20the%20land%20would%20be%20turned%20over%20and%20which%20would%20build%20the%20Ram%20temple%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F21154340%2FBabri-Masjid-wikimedia.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-226304%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22351%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERear%20view%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%20before%20it%20was%20demolished.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20people%20have%20questioned%20how%20the%20government%20of%20a%20constitutionally%20secular%20state%20can%20set%20up%20a%20trust%20which%20would%20build%20the%20place%20of%20worship%20of%20a%20particular%20religion.%20Irrespective%20of%20such%20questions%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20court%20also%20ruled%20that%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992%20and%20the%20desecration%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201949%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20law.%20Therefore%20it%20is%20now%20a%20matter%20of%20stated%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20that%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20being%20built%20upon%20the%20original%20foundation%20of%20events%20which%20are%20illegal.%20We%20know%20how%20the%20mandir-masjid%20dispute%20has%20been%20used%20over%20the%20last%20decades%20by%20a%20particular%20set%20of%20people%20and%20by%20a%20particular%20political%20party%20for%20gaining%20power%20and%20how%20the%20denouement%20of%20this%20dispute%20will%20be%20milked%20by%20the%20same%20set%20of%20people%20to%20continue%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20it%20is%20widely%20represented%20as%20something%20representing%20the%20%E2%80%9Csentiment%E2%80%9D%20of%20Hindus%2C%20it%20is%20not%20something%20any%20right-thinking%20Hindu%20would%20be%20proud%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20backdrop%2C%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20a%20puja%20associated%20with%20a%20BJP%20leader%20would%20build%20a%20pandal%20representing%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20make%20much%20inroads%20into%20the%20puja%20organising%20scenario%20of%20Kolkata%2C%20dominated%20by%20Trinamool%20Congress%20stalwarts.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20puja%20organised%20officially%20by%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20Eastern%20Zonal%20Cultural%20Centre%20in%20Kolkata%20was%20a%20non-starter%20and%20was%20discontinued%20from%20this%20year.%20Except%20for%20some%20frivolous%20attempts%20by%20some%20Hindutva-affiliated%20organisations%20to%20organise%20pujas%20and%20draw%20some%20public%20attention%20(last%20year%20one%20such%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fat-hindu-mahasabha-durga-puja-a-mahishasur-which-looks-similar-to-mahatma-gandhi%5C%22%3Eattempt%20by%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20in%20Kolkata%20involved%20representing%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20as%20Mahishasura%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20had%20to%20be%20changed%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20pujas%20after%20a%20public%20outcry)%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%20has%20not%20had%20much%20participation%20in%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20celebrations%20in%20Bengal.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20understandable%20that%20they%20have%20latched%20on%20to%20this%20puja%20pandal%20representing%20the%20Ram%20temple%20to%20show%20that%20they%20have%20arrived%20in%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20scenario%20and%20use%20it%20for%20further%20communal%20polarisation%20and%20political%20gain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20not%20understandable%20is%20why%20a%20single%20word%20is%20not%20being%20said%20by%20anyone%20%E2%80%93%20either%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20or%20even%20the%20opposition%20CPI(M)%20and%20Congress%2C%20or%20the%20media%2C%20or%20the%20culturally%20sensitive%20intelligentsia%20of%20Bengal.%20No%20one%20has%20said%20yet%20that%20such%20a%20puja%20pandal%20actually%20goes%20completely%20against%20the%20traditions%20and%20the%20ethos%20of%20Durga%20Puja%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20which%20has%20always%20celebrated%20communal%20amity%20and%20friendship.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20pandal%20marking%20the%20subjugation%20and%20dishonour%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20cannot%20or%20should%20not%20be%20a%20centrepiece%20of%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20celebrations%20in%20Kolkata.%20There%20are%20multiple%20Durga%20Pujas%20in%20Kolkata%20which%20are%20organised%20jointly%20by%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20there%20are%20even%20Durga%20Pujas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fsociety%2Fram-temple-ayodhya-khidirpur-muslims-durga-puja%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Eheld%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20Khidirpur%20and%20Metiaburuj%20where%20the%20entire%20organising%20committee%20is%20Muslim%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHas%20anyone%20thought%20about%20what%20these%20organisers%20may%20be%20thinking%20of%20when%20they%20see%20lakhs%20of%20people%20visiting%20this%20pandal%20and%20the%20news%20reporters%20gushing%20on%20television%20about%20it%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWill%20Muslim%20families%20who%20pandal%20hop%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20just%20like%20Hindu%20families%2C%20want%20to%20visit%20this%20pandal%20or%20are%20Muslims%20not%20welcome%20there%20at%20all%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20troubling%20sign%20of%20the%20times%20that%20mass%20sentiment%2C%20itself%20moulded%20carefully%20by%20propaganda%20in%20mainstream%20and%20social%20media%2C%20can%20wash%20away%20all%20conscientious%20thought%20and%20opinions.%20The%20reason%20why%20the%20TMC%2C%20CPI(M)%20and%20Congress%2C%20have%20remained%20silent%20about%20this%20travesty%20is%20that%20none%20of%20them%20would%20probably%20wish%20to%20alienate%20what%20they%20consider%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20voters%E2%80%9D.%20The%20intellectuals%20have%20kept%20quiet%20because%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20get%20into%20trouble.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20one%20bothered%20when%20constitutional%20functionaries%20were%20visiting%20the%20pandal%20because%20it%20was%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20faith.%20But%20it%20does%20not%20change%20the%20fact%20that%20such%20a%20celebration%20is%20in%20complete%20dissonance%20with%20what%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20festival%20in%20Bengal%20stands%20for.%20Unless%20acknowledged%20as%20such%2C%20it%20will%20open%20the%20floodgates%20for%20this%20very%20festival%20to%20be%20used%20for%20communal%20polarisation%20and%20destruction%20of%20communal%20harmony%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPartho%20Sarothi%20Ray%C2%A0is%20an%20academic%20and%20activist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697883810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161334%2FScreenshot-2023-10-18-at-4.13.24%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-durga-puja-kolkata%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20pandal%20marking%20the%20subjugation%20and%20dishonour%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20goes%20against%20the%20very%20ethos%20of%20the%20festivities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-durga-puja-kolkata%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arab%20leaders%20denounce%20Israel%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20as%20risks%20to%20region%20rise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697883507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104607513%2Cimgsize-1164901.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Farab-leaders-denounce-israel-attacks-on-gaza-as-risks-to-region-rise%2Farticleshow%2F104607294.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104607294.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EArab%20leaders%20gathered%20at%20the%20Cairo%20Peace%20Summit%20to%20condemn%20Israel's%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20and%20call%20for%20renewed%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20a%20Middle%20East%20peace%20settlement.%20Jordan's%20King%20Abdullah%20criticized%20the%20global%20silence%20on%20Israel's%20attacks%20and%20urged%20a%20fair%20approach%20to%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict.%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20affirmed%20that%20Palestinians%20would%20not%20be%20displaced%20or%20driven%20off%20their%20land.%20The%20summit%20aims%20to%20prevent%20a%20wider%20regional%20war%2C%20but%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20produce%20a%20joint%20statement%20due%20to%20sensitivities%20around%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20mentioning%20Hamas's%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Farab-leaders-denounce-israel-attacks-on-gaza-as-risks-to-region-rise%2Farticleshow%2F104607294.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Farab-leaders-denounce-israel-attacks-on-gaza-as-risks-to-region-rise%2Famp_articleshow%2F104607294.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Farab-leaders-denounce-israel-attacks-on-gaza-as-risks-to-region-rise%2Famp_articleshow%2F104607294.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20The%20Brave%20Six%20Who%20Stood%20Beneath%20An%20Exploding%20Nuclear%20Bomb%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20has%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20progress%20in%20developing%20nuclear%20power%20in%20the%20past%20few%20decades.%20It%20all%20started%20with%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20the%20world%20has%20crossed%20many%20milestones%2C%20making%20nuclear%20weapons%20more%20potent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20nuclear%20bombs%20were%20dropped%20on%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%2C%20the%20world%20witnessed%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20atomic%20age.%20Subsequently%2C%20extensive%20research%20and%20development%20efforts%20have%20been%20dedicated%20to%20advancing%20these%20formidable%20capabilities.%20To%20assess%20the%20impact%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%20on%20humans%2C%20the%20US%20undertook%20an%20exceptionally%20audacious%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fkrulwich%2F2012%2F07%2F16%2F156851175%2Ffive-men-agree-to-stand-directly-under-an-exploding-nuclear-bomb%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENPR%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20July%2019%2C%201957%2C%20five%20Air%20Force%20officers%20and%20one%20photographer%20stood%20together%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20ground%20about%2065%20miles%20northwest%20of%20Las%20Vegas.%20They'd%20marked%20the%20spot%20%26quot%3BGround%20Zero%2C%20Population%205%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20hand-lettered%20sign%20hammered%20into%20the%20soft%20ground%20right%20next%20to%20them.%20In%20a%20video%20from%20that%20time%2C%20two%20F-89%20jets%20roar%20into%20view%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20shoots%20off%20a%20nuclear%20missile%20carrying%20an%20atomic%20warhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20wait.%20There%20is%20a%20countdown%3B%2018%2C500%20feet%20above%20them%2C%20the%20missile%20is%20detonated%20and%20blows%20up.%20Which%20means%20these%20men%20intentionally%20stood%20directly%20underneath%20an%20exploding%202-kiloton%20nuclear%20bomb.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20at%20the%20key%20moment%20(he's%20wearing%20sunglasses)%2C%20looks%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FBlE1BdOAfVc%3Fsi%3DGLTUrLpyIdjBQE2W%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smithsonianmag.com%2Fsmart-news%2Fsix-guys-stood-at-nuclear-ground-zero-and-lived-to-tell-the-tale-4431750%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESmithsonian%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20five%20guys%20were%20Colonel%20Sidney%20Bruce%2C%20Lieutenant%