up%20the%20appeal%20for%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20March%2027%20order%20became%20public%2C%20tribal%20bodies%20launched%20protests%20across%20the%20state%2C%20which%20soon%20turned%20into%20a%20never-ending%20ethnic%20conflict%20with%20a%20clear%20division%20between%20Meiteis%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20Kukis%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20five-month-long%20violence%20has%20so%20far%20claimed%20180%20people%20and%20displaced%20lakhs%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20violence%20began%20on%20May%203%2C%20various%20tribal%20bodies%2C%20led%20by%20the%20All%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Union%2C%20moved%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20seeking%20leave%20to%20file%20a%20third-party%20appeal%20against%20the%20controversial%20order%20as%20an%20aggrieved%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20on%20October%2017%2C%20the%20court%20acceded%20to%20their%20appeal.%20%E2%80%9CTaking%20into%20consideration%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20arguments%20advanced%20by%20the%20learned%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20the%20parties%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20examined%20and%20decided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20materials%20available%20in%20the%20connected%20writ%20appeal%20and%20writ%20petition%20and%20taking%20into%20consideration%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20grievances%20raised%20by%20the%20applicants%2C%20we%20are%20inclined%20to%20grant%20leave%20sought%20by%20the%20applicants%20in%20the%20present%20application%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-hc-allows-tribal-bodies-to-appeal-against-order-on-st-status-for-meiteis%2Farticle67442711.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20tribal%20bodies%2C%20advocate%20Colin%20Gonsalves%20had%20faulted%20the%20controversial%20order%2C%20stating%20that%20Meiteis%E2%80%99%20claim%20to%20the%20ST%20status%20does%20not%20have%20merit%20and%20that%20the%20community%20has%20nowhere%20claimed%20to%20be%20backward%2C%20which%20is%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20claiming%20ST%20status.%20In%20their%20petition%2C%20the%20tribal%20bodies%20had%20also%20said%20that%20granting%20Meiteis%E2%80%99s%20ST%20status%20would%20mean%20snatching%20away%20the%20rights%20and%20benefits%20of%20existing%20STs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGonsalves%20had%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20tribal%20bodies%20had%20not%20been%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20present%20their%20views%20before%20passing%20the%20March%2027%20order.%20Not%20allowing%20them%20to%20appeal%20the%20order%20would%20affect%20their%20rights%20as%20an%20aggrieved%20party%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20raised%20no%20objections%20to%20allowing%20tribal%20bodies%20to%20appeal%20the%20order%2C%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%2C%20however%2C%20opposed%20the%20appeal%20against%20the%20order.%20The%20Singh%20government%2C%20like%20the%20Meitei%20Tribes%20Union%2C%20had%20said%20tribal%20unions%20cannot%20be%20considered%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Caggrieved%20party%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20instant%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20Meitei%20Tribes%20Union%E2%80%99s%20review%20petition%20is%20also%20pending%20before%20the%20high%20court%2C%20where%20tribal%20bodies%20have%20also%20been%20made%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697881846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25174440%2Fimage-1084.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-hc-allows-tribal-bodies-to-appeal-against-controversial-order-on-st-status-for-meiteis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20order%20proved%20to%20be%20an%20immediate%20trigger%20plunging%20the%20state%20into%20a%20nearly%20five-month-long%20ethnic%20violence%2C%20starting%20on%20May%203.%20The%20court%20on%20March%2027%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20recommend%20ST%20status%20for%20Meiteis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-hc-allows-tribal-bodies-to-appeal-against-controversial-order-on-st-status-for-meiteis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20forgotten%20Israeli%20hostages%20kept%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20for%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697881614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FD01D%2Fproduction%2F_131477235_mediaitem131477234.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67165002%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20pain%20over%20some%20200%20people%20kidnapped%20by%20Hamas%20overshadows%20the%20years%20of%20waiting%20for%20two%20hostages%20and%20soldiers'%20remains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67165002%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67165002.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67165002.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22International%20Criminal%20Court%20heightens%20security%20after%20espionage%20cyber-attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697881403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104606441%2Cimgsize-642750.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Finternational-criminal-court-heightens-security-after-espionage-cyber-attack%2Farticleshow%2F104606341.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104606341.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(ICC)%20has%20increased%20its%20online%20security%20after%20experiencing%20a%20serious%20cyber%20security