for%20the%20crucial%20November%2025%20polls.%20The%20party%20leaders%20also%20discussed%20potential%20strategies%20for%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20elections%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20as%20the%20party%20hopes%20to%20break%20the%20state's%20revolving%20door%20trend%2C%20where%20the%20incumbent%20party%20has%20routinely%20been%20voted%20out%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20disagreement%20between%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Sachin%20Pilot%20complicates%20the%20scenario%2C%20cornering%20the%20party%20into%20resolving%20its%20leadership%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20appeared%20headed%20for%20reconciliation%20after%20several%20attempts%2C%20with%20both%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20Mr%20Pilot%20engaging%20in%20extensive%20discussions%20with%20senior%20party%20leaders%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20solving%20the%20Karnataka%20conundrum%20of%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20DK%20Shivakumar%20-%20who%20shared%20a%20somewhat%20similar%20equation%20-%20the%20party%20has%20managed%20to%20get%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20on%20board%20to%20meet%20Sachin%20Pilot's%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin%20Pilot%20had%20last%20month%20said%20that%20the%20party%20would%20fight%20the%20assembly%20elections%20%26quot%3Bunitedly%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20secure%20the%20mandate%2C%20the%20legislators%20and%20the%20leadership%20will%20decide%20on%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697881020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Fha2mctkg_ashok-gehlot-sachin-pilot-pti_625x300_04_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-gehlot-sachin-pilot-in-congress-1st-rajasthan-list-no-major-changes-4502318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20today%20released%20the%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20Rajasthan%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20Rajasthan%20elections%20are%20crucial%20for%20