rk%20where%20his%20homecoming%20rally%20is%20due%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20has%20been%20touted%20for%20months%20by%20the%20PML-N%2C%20whose%20leaders%20hope%20Sharif's%20political%20clout%20and%20%26quot%3Bman%20of%20the%20soil%26quot%3B%20swagger%20will%20revive%20its%20flagging%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20term%20of%20Sharif%20--%20who%20came%20to%20power%20riding%20on%20a%20triumphant%20victory%20in%202013%20--%20was%20scarred%20by%20upheavals.%20It%20started%20with%20the%20then-opposition-led%20months-long%20blockade%20of%20Islamabad%20and%20ended%20with%20his%20disqualification%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202017.%20The%20court%20ruling%20followed%20months%20of%20hearings%20in%20a%20case%20instigated%20by%20the%20%26quot%3BPanama%20Papers%26quot%3B%20leaks%2C%20related%20to%20alleged%20corruption%20during%20his%20previous%20two%20terms%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Islamabad%20High%20Court%20granted%20protective%20bail%20to%20Sharif%20until%20Tuesday%2C%20removing%20the%20threat%20of%20immediate%20arrest%20when%20he%20lands%20back%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697880960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Fm6qdlvuo_nawaz-sharif-pti_625x300_30_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-returns-to-pakistan-after-4-year-self-imposed-exile-in-uk-4502254%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three-time%20Pakistan%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20returned%20home%20today%20after%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%2C%20and%20primed%20to%20make%20a%20political%20comeback%20ahead%20of%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-returns-to-pakistan-after-4-year-self-imposed-exile-in-uk-4502254%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-returns-to-pakistan-after-4-year-self-imposed-exile-in-uk-4502254%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnawaz-sharif-returns-to-pakistan-after-4-year-self-imposed-exile-in-uk-4502254%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20%26quot%3B3D%26quot%3B%20Man%20On%20A%20Mission%20-%20by%20Vinay%20Sahasrabuddhe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20a%20political%20leader%20second%20only%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20evoking%20popular%20interest%2C%20curiosity%20and%20deep%20respect%3B%20will%20turn%2059%20on%20October%2022.%20Till%202014%2C%20he%20was%20known%20only%20as%20the%20ex-Gujarat%20Home%20Minister%20who%20later%20rose%20to%20become%20BJP%20General%20Secretary%20in%202013-14.%20But%20post%202014%2C%20after%20becoming%20the%20BJP's%20youngest%20National%20President%2C%20there%20was%20no%20looking%20back%20for%20this%20'Man-always-on-a-Mission%2C'%20known%20for%20exceptional%20leadership%20qualities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20dedicated%20RSS%20Swayamsevak%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20a%20multi-dimensional%20personality.%20Unabashedly%20taking%20pride%20in%20Indian%20culture%2C%20his%20drawing%20room%20always%20had%20two%20portraits%3B%20that%20of%20Arya%20Chanakya%20and%20Swatanryaveer%20Sawarkar.%20Known%20for%20his%20courage%20of%20conviction%2C%20he%20has%20become%20famous%20for%20three%20Ds%20-%20dexterity%2C%20decisiveness%20and%20above%20all%2C%20dedication%20to%20his%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Amit%20Shah%20one%20comes%20across%20a%20rare%20combination%20of%20organisational%20skills%20and%20strategic%20thinking.%20Through%20his%20unparalleled%20dexterity%20in%20various%20aspects%20of%20science%20of%20organisation%2C%20he%20has%20contributed%20remarkably%20to%20the%20BJP%20organisation%20while%20helming%20this%20Largest%20Political%20Party%20of%20the%20World.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20started%20his%20tenure%20with%20a%20mass-membership%20campaign%2C%20making%20the%20BJP%20the%20first%20political%20party%20to%20use%20smart-phones%20for%20enrolment%20of%20party%20members.%20From%2010%20founding%20members%20of%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20during%20Amit%20Shah's%20tenure%2C%20India's%20only%20ideology-based%20party%20with%20a%20pan-India%20presence%2C%20reached%2010%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20unquestionable%20dedication%20to%20ideology%20makes%20him%20work%20untiringly%20for%20long%20hours%2C%20whether%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20organisation%20or%20that%20of%20the%20government.%20And%20importantly%2C%20he%20not%20only%20understands%20but%20also%20strives%20to%20make%20others%20understand%20the%20Mission%20of%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BRemember%2C%20we%20are%20not%20running%20an%20election%20winning%20machine%2C%20we%20are%20essentially%20a%20mission-oriented%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20used%20to%20stress%20eloquently%20during%20his%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20two%20tenures%20of%20three%20years%20each%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20achieved%20historic%20firsts.%20He%20created%20some%2019%20different%20departments%20for%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20party%2C%20revived%20a%20system%20of%20structured%20organisational%20tours%2C%20remarkably%20tried%20to%20make%20the%20BJP's%20presence%20not%20just%20felt%2C%20but%20also%20productive%20in%20previously%20barren%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Telangana%20and%20more%20particularly%2C%20West%20Bengal%3B%20and%20added%20a%20new%20%3Cem%3ESewa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(service%20to%20Humanity)%20dimension%20to%20party%20work.%20It%20was%20during%20his%20tenure%20that%20the%20party%20started%20service%20-%20projects%20like%20saving%20the%20girl%20child%3B%20eradication%20of%20manual%20scavenging%20and%20cleaning%20of%20rivers%20in%20respective%20districts%2Fregions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20institution%20builder's%20approach%3B%20Amit%20Shah%20created%20a%20new%20building%20for%20the%20BJP's%20headquarters%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20well-equipped%20with%20all%20facilities%20including%20libraries%3B%20both%20physical%20and%20digital.%20In%20fact%2C%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20organisation%20needs%20its%20own%20adequately%20large%20office%20spaces%3B%20Amit%20Shah%20embarked%20on%20a%20office-building-construction%20spree%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20party%20office%20infrastructures%20from%20Aizawl%20to%20Anantnag%20and%20Kozhikode%20to%20Kohima.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20knows%20very%20well%20that%20the%20devil%20is%20in%20the%20details.%20It%20was%20because%20of%20this%20basic%20understanding%20that%20he%20personally%20reviewed%20the%20functioning%20of%20party%20units%20at%20the%20booth%20level%20and%20at%20the%20end%2C%20came%20out%20with%20a%2023-point%20action%20plan%20for%20the%20party's%20booth%20in-charge%20%3Cem%3EKaryakartas.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20ability%20to%20take%20courageous%20decisions%20puts%20him%20in%20a%20different%20league.%20His%20making%20an%20alliance%20with%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20party%20in%20Kashmir%20ensured%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20first%20government%20with%20BJP's%20participation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20something%20nobody%20could%20have%20imagined.%20Like%20his%20mentor%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Amit%20Bhai%20too%20is%20known%20for%20taking%20legitimate%20risks%20and%20as%20it%20happens%3B%20risk%20takers%20are%20always%20rewarded%20in%20politics.%20His%20ability%20to%20take%20hard%20decisions%20and%20make%20strategic%20moves%20with%20dexterity%20eventually%20saw%20a%20record%20number%20of%2013%20states%20where%20the%20BJP%20acquired%20power%20during%20the%20first%20three%20years%20of%20his%20president-ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20all%20three%20Ds%20were%20on%20full%20display%20during%20the%20last%204.5%20years%20of%20his%20tenure%20as%20Home%20Minister.%20Earlier%2C%20when%20he%20was%20Minister%20in%20Gujarat%20handling%20portfolios%20like%20Home%2C%20Panchayati%20Raj%2C%20Prohibition%2C%20and%20Transport%20he%20became%20known%20for%20many%20significant%20initiatives.%20His%20efforts%20for%20systemic%20changes%20for%20fixing%20accountability%20of%20lower%20bureaucracy%20in%20Panchayati%20Raj%20institutions%2C%20creating%20modern%20forensic%20laboratories%20and%20making%20coastal%20policing%20effective%20and%20result-oriented%20earned%20him%20great%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Home%20Minister%20he%20has%20worked%20overtime%20to%20ensure%20that%20India%20becomes%20terror-free.%20Data-driven%20deterrence%20and%20discipline%20of%20an%20exceptionally%20high%20order%20are%20the%20two%20points%20he%20has%20refused%20to%20compromise%20on.%20Within%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20the%20deadly%20Pulwama%20attack%20in%202019%2C%20militancy%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20consistently%20on%20the%20wane.%20Despite%20the%20apprehensions%20of%20many%2C%20organising%20a%20meeting%20of%20G-20%20right%20in%20Srinagar%20was%20also%20reflective%20of%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20courage%20of%20conviction.%20In%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20people%20have%20almost%20forgotten%20the%20spectre%20of%20clashes%20between%20public%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20statistics%20also%20show%20that%20youths%20are%20now%20more%20interested%20in%20joining%20thr%20military%20than%20militancy.%20Official%20records%20say%20between%202018%20and%202022%2C%20deaths%20of%20security%20personnel%20fell%20by%2066%20per%20cent%2C%20whereas%20terror%20attacks%2Fencounters%20fell%20by%2045%20per%20cent.%20Changes%20in%20the%20ground%20situation%20have%20also%20resulted%20in%20more%20tourists%20visiting%20this%20heaven%20on%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20is%20more%20remarkable%20about%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20his%20long%20term%20vision%20and%20clarity%20about%20the%20objectives.%20Recently%2C%20at%20a%20Chintan%20Shivir%20of%20his%20Ministry%2C%20he%20rightly%20emphasised%20on%20the%20need%20to%20visualise%20the%20challenges%20of%20the%20future%20and%20find%20their%20advance%20solutions.%20He%20has%20always%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20enhanced%20use%20of%20AI%20while%20utilising%20the%20Crime%20and%20Criminal%20Tracking%20Network%20and%20Systems%20(CCTNS)%20database%20for%20critical%20analysis%20of%20crimes%2C%20making%20cities%20more%20safe%20for%20women%2C%20children%20and%20vulnerable%20sections.%20After%20the%20introduction%20of%20new%20reforms%2C%20this%20portal%20today%20provides%20for%20digitisation%20of%20data%20related%20to%20FIR%20registration%2C%20investigation%2C%20and%20charge%20sheets%20eventually%20developing%20a%20national%20database%20of%20crime%20and%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20absolute%20workaholic%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20is%20never%20short%20of%20motivation%20due%20to%20his%20clarity%20of%20thoughts.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20political%20parties%20need%20to%20be%20assessed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20philosophy%2C%20internal%20democracy%20in%20their%20organisation%20and%20their%20performance%20when%20in%20power.%20'We%20are%20not%20here%20to%20make%20somebody%20a%20Minister%20and%20some%20other%20person%20a%20bank%20chairperson%2C'%20he%20had%20said%20many%20times%20without%20mincing%20words.%20Later%2C%20in%20a%20monograph%20%26quot%3BWhy%20BJP%20is%20in%20Politics%26quot%3B%20he%20also%20reminded%20party%20cadres%20that%20'the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20re-establish%20a%20strong%20element%20of%20integrity%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20this%20country.%20Transparent%20governance%2C%20participatory%20democracy%20and%20all-inclusive%20harmonious%20society%20are%20our%20top%20priorities.%20We%20wish%20that%20India%20should%20become%20so%20prosperous%20that%20it%20would%20be%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20World.'%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVinay%20Sahasrabuddhe%20is%20former%20MP%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20columnist%2C%20besides%20being%20President%20of%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Cultural%20Relations%20(ICCR)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697880900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F4po152tk_amit-shah-pti_625x300_11_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Famit-shah-3d-man-on-a-mission-by-vinay-sahasrabuddhe-4502182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Known%20for%20his%20courage%20of%20conviction%2C%20he%20has%20become%20famous%20for%20three%20Ds%20-%20dexterity%2C%20decisiveness%20and%20above%20all%2C%20dedication%20to%20his%20ideology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Famit-shah-3d-man-on-a-mission-by-vinay-sahasrabuddhe-4502182%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meryl%20Streep%2C%20Don%20Gummer%20secretly%20separated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697880665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104605992%2Cimgsize-22624.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fmeryl-streep-and-husband-don-gummer-have-been-secretly-separated-for-6-years-reports%2Farticleshow%2F104605870.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104605870.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMeryl%20Streep%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Don%20Gummer%2C%20have%20officially%20separated%20after%20nearly%2045%20years%20together.%20Despite%20living%20separate%20lives%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20the%20couple%20still%20holds%20deep%20affection%20for%20one%20another.%20Known%20for%20their%20private%20relationship%2C%20the%20news%20of%20their%20separation%20comes%20as%20a%20surprise.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Jada%20Pinkett%20Smith%20and%20Will%20Smith%20have%20also%20been%20living%20separately%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20years%20but%20ha