ach%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20measure.%20An%20angry%20India%2C%20which%20termed%20the%20allegations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%E2%80%9D%2C%20also%20stopped%20all%20visa%20services%20in%20Canada%20and%20asked%20the%20north%20American%20nation%20to%20reduce%20its%20diplomatic%20strength%20to%20be%20in%20line%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20numbers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20before%20the%20second%20deadline%20of%20October%2020%2C%20Canada%20repatriated%20the%20majority%20of%20its%20diplomats%20from%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20confirm%20that%20the%20diplomatic%20status%20of%20the%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20who%20have%20left%20India%20has%20been%20revoked%20as%20of%20today%2C%20October%2020%2C%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20Emily%20Williams%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20Canadian%20foreign%20minister%20Joly%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle-world-should-be-worried-about-indias-threat-to-strip-canadian%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20quoted%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Globe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20responded%20through%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37201%2FParity%2Bin%2BCanadian%2Bdiplomatic%2Bpresence%2Bin%2BIndia%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20its%20actions%20%E2%80%9Cimplementing%20this%20parity%20(in%20diplomatic%20strength)%20are%20fully%20consistent%20with%20Article%2011.1%20of%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-calls-canadas-consulate-move-unilateral-clarifies-parity-only-for-diplomats-in-capitals%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20on%20the%20night%20of%20October%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Indian%20official%20sources%20further%20buttressed%20this%20stance%2C%20insisting%20that%20it%20was%20not%20only%20in%20line%20with%20VCDR%2C%20but%20also%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20legislation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20defence%20didn%E2%80%99t%20cut%20much%20ice%20in%20Washington%20and%20London%2C%20both%20partners%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Five%20Eyes%E2%80%99%20intelligence%20network%20with%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Have%20urged%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fdeparture-of-canadian-diplomats-from-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20state%20department%20spokesperson%20Mathew%20Miller%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20that%20Washington%20was%20%E2%80%9Cconcerned%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20departure%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20%E2%80%9Cin%20response%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20demand%20of%20Canada%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CResolving%20differences%20requires%20diplomats%20on%20the%20ground.%20We%20have%20urged%20the%20Indian%20government%20not%20to%20insist%20upon%20a%20reduction%20in%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20presence%20and%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Canadian%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20Miller%20stated%20that%20the%20US%20%E2%80%9Cexpect%5Bs%5D%20India%20to%20uphold%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%201961%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%2C%20including%20with%20respect%20to%20privileges%20and%20immunities%20enjoyed%20by%20accredited%20members%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20mission%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Unilateral%20move%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fdeparture-of-canadian-diplomats-from-india-fcdo-response%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UK%20foreign%20office%20stated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%20did%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20agree%20with%20the%20decisions%20taken%20by%C2%A0the%20Indian%20government%20that%C2%A0have%C2%A0resulted%20in%20a%C2%A0number%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20departing%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20British%20Foreign%2C%20Commonwealth%20and%20Development%20Office%20bluntly%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20unilateral%20removal%20of%20the%20privileges%20and%20immunities%20that%20provide%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20diplomats%20is%20not%20consistent%20with%20the%20principles%20or%20the%20effective%20functioning%20of%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20noted%20that%20all%20states%20were%20expected%20to%20%E2%80%9Cuphold%20their%20obligations%20under%20the%201961%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20UK%20reiterated%20that%20India%20should%20%E2%80%9Cengage%20with%20Canada%20on%20its%20independent%20investigation%20into%20the%20death%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Contravene%20a%20very%20fundamental%20principle%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20foreign%20minister%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Ftrudeau-india-making-life-difficult-1.7002961%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECanadian%20prime%20minister%20accused%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20violating%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20international%20diplomacy%2C%20which%20he%20said%20should%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20whole%20world%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20them%20choosing%20to%20contravene%20a%20very%20fundamental%20principle%20of%20international%20law%20and%20diplomacy.%20It%20is%20something%20that%20all%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20should%20be%20very%20worried%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trudeau%20told%20reporters%20in%20Brampton%2C%20Canada%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20October%2021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20parity%20has%20hurt%20Indo-Canadians%20and%20Indians%20wanting%20to%20study%20or%20work%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20making%20it%20unbelievably%20difficult%20for%20life%20as%20usual%20to%20continue%20for%20millions%20of%20people%20in%20India%20and%20in%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%20what%20New%20Delhi%20has%20done%20%E2%80%9Chas%20me%20very%20concerned%20for%20the%20well-being%20and%20happiness%20of%20millions%20of%20Canadians%20who%20trace%20their%20origins%20to%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOCI%20demand%20upsurge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Ftoronto%2Findian-visa-brampton-lineup-1.6999972%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520India%2527s%2520festive%2520season%2520approaches%2COverseas%2520Citizens%2520of%2520India%2520card.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20report%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECBC%20news%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20stated%20that%20there%20was%20an%20upsurge%20in%20demand%20for%20the%20Overseas%20Citizens%20of%20India%20(OCI)%20card%2C%20with%20Indian-origin%20Canadians%20camping%20around%20the%20clock%20outside%20the%20OCI%20office%20in%20Brampton%20to%20be%20able%20to%20submit%20their%20applications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20only%20service%20that%20India%20has%20not%20suspended%20after%20all%20other%20operations%20were%20suspended%20for%20Canadian%20nationals.%20With%20an%20OCI%20card%2C%20a%20foreign%20national%20can%20visit%20and%20stay%20in%20India%20as%20long%20as%20they%20want.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Canadian%20decision%20to%20stop%20in-person%20services%20at%20the%20three%20consulates%20will%20certainly%20impact%20thousands%20of%20Indians%2C%20with%20officials%20in%20Canada%20estimating%20that%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20backlog%20of%2017%2C500%20applications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELate%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20Indian%20officials%20had%20claimed%20India%20had%20only%20sought%20parity%20between%20the%20two%20main%20missions%20in%20Ottawa%20and%20New%20Delhi%20and%20not%20in%20the%20three%20consulates.%20They%20described%20that%20the%20Canadian%20move%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunilateral%20and%20not%20related%20to%20implementation%20of%20parity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697879249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19230651%2FH20230910138622.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-diplomats-us-united-kingdom-canada-vienna-convention%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20had%20announced%20on%20October%2019%20that%20it%20was%20withdrawing%2041%20diplomats%2C%20leaving%20only%2021%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-diplomats-us-united-kingdom-canada-vienna-convention%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ganapath%20box%20office%20collection%20day%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697879056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104605361%2Cimgsize-50086.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fganapath-box-office-collection-day-1-tiger-shroffs-film-mints-less-than-rs-3-crore%2Farticleshow%2F104605340.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A