inning%20of%20a%20sustained%20effort%20to%20provide%20aid%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20However%2C%20Israel%20has%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20potential%20misuse%20of%20fuel%20brought%20into%20Gaza%20by%20Hamas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ffirst-of-20-aid-trucks-enter-besieged-gaza-from-egypt%2Farticleshow%2F104605296.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ffirst-of-20-aid-trucks-enter-besieged-gaza-from-egypt%2Famp_articleshow%2F104605296.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ffirst-of-20-aid-trucks-enter-besieged-gaza-from-egypt%2Famp_articleshow%2F104605296.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Daily%20Despatch%3A%20Hamas%20Releases%202%20Israeli-American%20Hostages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fa30ro6f_israelhamas-war_625x300_21_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20surprise%20move%20late%20Friday%20night%2C%20Hamas%20released%20two%20of%20the%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20held%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%207.%20The%20hostages%2C%20Judith%20(59)%20and%20Natalie%20Raanan%20(17)%2C%20a%20mother%20and%20daughter%20from%20Chicago%2C%20are%20Israeli-American%20citizens.%20They%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Red%20Cross%20and%20then%20transferred%20to%20the%20US%20Embassy%20in%20Jerusalem.%20In%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20Hamas%20claimed%20that%20the%20sudden%20release%20of%20two%20hostages%20was%20spurred%20by%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20reasons%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Israeli%20media%2C%20Natalie's%20father%20Uri%20Raanan%20said%20his%20daughter%20felt%20fine%2C%20and%20that%20no%20harm%20was%20done%20to%20her%20while%20she%20was%20held%20hostage.%26quot%3B%20She%20is%20happy%20to%20be%20back%20home%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20she%20will%20be%20able%20to%20celebrate%20her%20birthday%20next%20week%20in%20Chicago%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJudith%20and%20Natalie%20Raanan%20arrived%20in%20Israel%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20ago%20to%20celebrate%20the%2085th%20birthday%20of%20Judith's%20mother%20Tamar%20Levitan%20in%20the%20southern%20kibbutz%20of%20Nahal%20Oz.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20October%207%2C%20the%20kibbutz%20was%20attacked%20by%20Hamas%20and%20the%20two%20women%20were%20among%20those%20taken%20hostage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20two%20hostages%20has%20raised%20hope%20that%20more%20will%20be%20freed%20by%20Hamas.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20expected%20Israeli%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20situation%20we%20have%20never%20seen%20before.%20Many%20Israelis%20are%20asking%20the%20army%20to%20delay%20the%20ground%20offensive%20in%20order%20to%20prioritize%20the%20release%20of%20the%20many%20hostages.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eran%20Etzion%2C%20former%20head%20of%20policy%20planning%20at%20Israel's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Channel%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20a%20journalist%20asked%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20whether%20Israel%20should%20delay%20its%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20until%20more%20hostages%20are%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20replied%2C%20but%20later%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Ben%20LaBolt%20stated%20that%20Biden%20did%20not%20fully%20hear%20the%20question%20due%20to%20noise%20from%20the%20engines%20of%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20that%20the%20President%20thought%20he%20was%20replying%20to%20whether%20he%20would%20like%20to%20see%20more%20hostages%20freed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Army%20Spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20countered%20Hamas'%20claim%20that%20the%20two%20hostages%20were%20freed%20because%20of%20humanitarian%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20is%20presenting%20itself%20to%20the%20world%20as%20one%20that%20releases%20hostages%20for%20humanitarian%20reasons%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20a%20murderous%20terror%20group%2C%20which%20at%20this%20hour%20is%20holding%20babies%2C%20children%2C%20women%2C%20and%20elderly%20captive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%20He%20also%20hinted%20that%20the%20fighting%20would%20take%20many%20more%20weeks.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20at%20brokering%20a%20ceasefire%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20representatives%20from%20a%20long%20list%20of%20countries%20will%20meet%20in%20Egyptian%20capital%20Cairo%20on%20Saturday.%20On%20Friday%2C%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20announced%20that%20he%20had%20invited%20top%20officials%20from%20Europe%2C%20Qatar%20and%20Turkey%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20peace%20summit.%20No%20breakthrough%20is%20expected%20from%20the%20summit%20because%20major%20players%20of%20the%20latest%20crisis%20are%20not%20taking%20part.%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Hamas%20or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20Iran%2C%20are%20all%20absent%20as%20the%20leaders%20meet%20in%20Cairo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20Politico%2C%20veteran%20Lebanese%20politician%20Walid%20Jumblatt%20expressed%20skepticism%20over%20the%20Cairo%20summit.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20non-players%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20the%20countries%20taking%20part.%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20have%20any%20influence.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMass%20protests%20were%20held%20on%20Friday%20in%20support%20of%20Hamas%20and%20Gaza%20in%20Cairo.%20At%20some%20point%20the%20protests%20even%20spread%20to%20Tahrir%20Square%2C%20where%20protests%20in%202011%20overthrew%20former%20President%20Hosni%20Mubarak.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20and%20Jordan's%20King%20Abdullah%20II%20have%20serious%20security%20concerns%20about%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20especially%20regarding%20the%20possible%20displacement%20of%20the%20Gazan%20population.%20Both%20leaders%20have%20strongly%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20letting%20Palestinian%20refugees%20into%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt.%20%26quot%3BNo%20refugees%20in%20Jordan%2C%20no%20refugees%20in%20Egypt%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Jordanian%20monarch%20said%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%20also%20warned%20that%20an%20attempt%20to%20push%20Gazans%20into%20Egypt%20would%20wreck%20peace%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGazans%20are%20still%20waiting%20for%20aid%20trucks%20to%20pass%20into%20Gaza%20from%20Egypt.%20Trucks%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20of%20the%20Rafah%20border%20are%20ready%20to%20move%20into%20Gaza%2C%20but%20so%20far%2C%20there's%20no%20green%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20had%20on%20Wednesday%20accepted%20Biden's%20request%20to%20allow%20some%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20be%20delivered.%20But%20as%20of%20late%20Friday%20night%2C%20no%20aid%20trucks%20had%20passed%20the%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%2C%20Israel%20has%20issued%20an%20evacuation%20order%20for%20the%20al-Quds%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20city.%20The%20hospital%20is%20currently%20treating%20approximately%20400%20patients%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20internally%20displaced%20people%20are%20staying%20at%20the%20hospital%20or%20its%20close%20vicinity%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Red%20Crescent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Army%20denies%20any%20new%20evacuation%20order%20and%20argues%20that%20the%20first%20order%20given%20a%20week%20ago%20to%20the%20population%20of%20north%20Gaza%20is%20still%20valid.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Euro-Med%20Monitor%2C%20at%20least%204%2C079%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20October%207.%20Among%20the%20dead%20are%201%2C413%20children%20and%20806%20women.%20More%20than%2015%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20injured.%20Some%201%2C400%20Israelis%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20villages%20on%20October%207.%20The%20Israeli%20medical%20team%20of%20first%20responders%20on%20Friday%20announced%20that%20they%20are%20still%20recovering%20bodies%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20deadly%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Friday%2C%20attacks%20continued%20on%20Israel's%20northern%20border%20to%20Lebanon.%20The%20Lebanese%20Shiite%20Hezbollah%20militia%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attacks%20that%20included%20at%20least%2030%20rockets%20and%20several%20anti-tank%20missiles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Force%20said%20it%20carried%20out%20airstrikes%20against%20a%20number%20of%20Hezbollah%20sites%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20in%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20previously%20unseen%20development%2C%20the%20Iran-backed%20Yemenite%20Houthi%20movement%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20fired%20multiple%20missiles%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Israel%20late%20Thursday.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20USS%20Carney%2C%20a%20US%20Navy-guided%20missile%20destroyer%20in%20the%20northern%20Red%20Sea%2C%20shot%20down%20the%20missiles%20and%20drones%20launched%20by%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697878500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F8r9n32r8_israelhamas-war_625x300_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-hamas-releases-2-israeli-american-hostages-4502281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20surprise%20move%20late%20Friday%20night%2C%20Hamas%20released%20two%20of%20the%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20held%20i