0these%20are%20the%20two%2C%20and%20your%20Thackeray%E2%80%99)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0At%20the%20time%20of%20submitting%20the%20charge%20sheet%20before%20the%20Borivali%20metropolitan%20magistrate%20court%2C%20the%20GRP%20told%20the%20court%20that%20Chaudhary%20was%20not%20brought%20to%20the%20court%20but%20produced%20through%20video%20conferencing%20as%20it%20might%20not%20be%20safe%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInitially%2C%20the%20railways%20had%20harped%20on%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20mental%20health%20but%20had%20eventually%20termed%20his%20act%20as%20a%20heinous%20crime.%20He%20was%20dismissed%20from%20service%20in%20the%20month%20of%20August.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Chaudhary%20was%20booked%20under%20Section%20302%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20murder%2C%20along%20with%20sections%20of%20the%20Arms%20Act%20and%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20his%20first%20production%20before%20a%20magistrate%20court%20on%20August%202%2C%20the%20police%20had%20chosen%20a%20diametrically%20opposite%20narrative%20to%20what%20was%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20The%20remand%20copy%20did%20not%20make%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20video%20that%20clearly%20showed%20his%20communally-charged%20speech.%20The%20remand%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20entirely%20focused%20on%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cillness%E2%80%9D%20and%20indicates%20his%20unstable%20mind%20which%20led%20him%20to%20conduct%20the%20extreme%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpolice-focuses-on-rpf-constables-mental-illness-erases-mention-of-possible-hate-crime-from-fir%5C%22%3EPolice%20Focuses%20on%20RPF%20Constable%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Mental%20Illness%E2%80%99%2C%20Erases%20Mention%20of%20Possible%20Hate%20Crime%20from%20FIR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20following%20criticism%2C%20the%20police%20had%20added%20sections%20153A%2C%20341%20and%20342%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20151%2C%20152%20and%20153%20of%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%20Section%20153%20A%20is%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpromoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20the%20police%20have%20now%20added%20sections%20like%20364%20(kidnapping%20for%20murder)%2C%20427%20(mischief%20and%20causing%20loss)%2C%20506%20(2)%20(death%20threats)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20Section%203%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Damage%20to%20Public%20Property%20Act.%20Although%20Meena%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20sections%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20have%20not%20been%20applied%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20managed%20a%20good%20number%20of%20both%20direct%20and%20circumstantial%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20case%20is%20next%20scheduled%20for%20hearing%20on%20November%202.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697875422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F16111107%2F5264934981_08748b0f32_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-railway-police-rpf-bjp-mental-illness%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20claimed%20that%20while%20senior%20ASI%20Tika%20Ram%20Meena%20could%20have%20been%20killed%20out%20of%20anger%2C%20the%20murders%20of%20the%20three%20Muslim%20men%20were%20selective%20in%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-railway-police-rpf-bjp-mental-illness%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22