C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fgarg_trupti%2Fstatus%2F1713861345026973977%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Elost%20no%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20troll%20Zubair%2C%20a%20marked%20guy%20for%20the%20right%20wing%20in%20India%20anyway%20for%20his%20continuous%20debunking%20of%20several%20of%20their%20communal%20claims.%20A%20fact-checker%20with%20a%20wrong%20name%2C%20of%20course.%20Off%20and%20on%2C%20FIRs%2C%20therefore%2C%20get%20filed%20against%20Zubair%2C%20prodding%20police%20in%20some%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20ruled%20state%20or%20the%20other%20to%20take%20them%20further.%20One%20such%20complaint%20had%20put%20him%20behind%20bars%20for%20some%20weeks%20not%20so%20long%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Israeli%20diplomat%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20stop%20Zubair%E2%80%99s%20work%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20troll%20army%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20had%20already%20set%20the%20tone%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20mouthing%20unwavering%20support%20for%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20straightjacketing%20Palestinians%20as%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhindutva-israel-tweets-palestine-conflict%5C%22%3EUnpacking%20the%20Hindutva%20Embrace%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20stand%20is%20typically%20hinged%20on%20the%20anti-Muslim%20ideology%20of%20the%20larger%20Sangh%20Parivar%2C%20and%20also%20its%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20language%2C%20one%20religion%20dream%20which%20brings%20them%20closer%20to%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20Hindutva%20Zion%2C%20a%20partner%20state%20of%20Israel%2C%20to%20paraphrase%20Faisal%20Devji%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hup.harvard.edu%2Fcatalog.php%3Fisbn%3D9780674072671%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMuslim%20Zion%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20title%20of%20his%20book%20on%20how%20Pakistan%20imagined%20itself.%20So%20also%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20imparting%20arms-training%20to%20all%20its%20young%20and%20able%2C%20which%20fits%20perfectly%20in%20support%20shown%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20K.B.%20Hedgewar%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20for%20the%20militarisation%20of%20the%20Hindu%20society%2C%20to%20eventually%20fight%20the%20Muslims.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20no%20rocket%20science%20that%20the%20reigning%20star%20of%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20has%20been%20inching%20closer%20to%20the%20Israeli%20far-right%20wing%20government%20and%20particularly%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20its%20controversial%20prime%20minister.%20The%20idea%20about%20Israel%2C%20a%20Jewish%20homeland%2C%20is%20a%20model%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20desperately%20wants%20to%20bring%20home%20to%20India%20in%20a%20Hindutva%20variant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlast%20from%20the%20past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20likes%20of%20Shoshnani%20must%20need%20reminding%20though%20is%20the%20pro-Nazi%20sentiment%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20contingent%20in%20the%201930s.%20Particularly%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20leader%20V.K.%20Savarkar%2C%20considered%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20flip%20here%20a%20few%20pages%20of%20history%20to%20help%20Shoshnani%20and%20his%20ilk%20do%20that%20reminding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Jerusalem%2C%20some%20years%20ago%2C%20walking%20through%20the%20largest%20Holocaust%20remembrance%20centre%2C%20Yad%20Vashem%2C%20my%20Hindu%20heart%20sank%20in%20shame%20when%20at%20one%20place%2C%20an%20audio%20visual%20exhibit%20flashed%20the%20Swastika%20to%20highlight%20that%20Hitler%20copied%20the%20symbol%20from%20the%20religion.%20That%20a%20sacred%20symbol%20of%20my%20religion%20was%20worn%20on%20the%20arms%20that%20aimed%20for%20the%20neck%20of%20thousands%20of%20innocent%20Jews%20including%20children%20did%20make%20me%20mumble%20under%20my%20breath%2C%20it%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20in%20my%20name.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21112644%2FDSC_2831_0.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21112644%2FDSC_2831_0.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21112644%2FDSC_2831_0-300x206.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681129%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EYad%20Vashem%2C%20The%20World%20Holocaust%20Remembrance%20Center.%20Photo%3A%20Yossi%20Ben%20David%2F%20Yad%20Vashem%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.yadvashem.org%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParallel%20to%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20Germany%2C%20in%20the%20India%20of%20the%201930s%2C%20top%20honchos%20of%20Hindutva%20were%2C%20however%2C%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Nazi%20leader%20and%20his%20annihilation%20of%20the%20Jews.%C2%A0%20The%20likes%20of%20Savarkar%20and%20M.S.%20Golwalkar%20were%20at%20odds%20with%20Congress%20leaders%20of%20the%20day%2C%20like%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20for%20not%20supporting%20the%20Nazis%20and%20the%20Fascism%20of%20Italy.%20Marzia%20Casolari%20in%20her%202023%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Shadow%20of%20Swastika%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Relationship%20Between%20Indian%20Radical%20Nationalism%2C%20Italian%20Fascism%20and%20Nazism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20writes%20that%20a%20month%20after%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%20anti-Jewish%20pogrom%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20Night%20of%20Broken%20Glass%E2%80%99%20took%20place%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpro-Hindu%20Mahasabha%20journals%20published%20articles%20in%20favour%20of%20German%20anti-Semitism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20further%20writes%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThis%20stance%20brought%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20into%20conflict%20with%20the%20Congress%20which%2C%20on%2012%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20December%20(1938)%2C%20made%20a%20statement%20containing%20clear%20references%20to%20recent%20European%20events.%20Within%20the%20Congress%2C%20only%20(Subhash%20Chandra)%20Bose%20opposed%20the%20party%20stance.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20in%20April%201939%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20support%20the%20party%20motion%20that%20Jews%20might%20find%20refuge%20in%20India.%20Savarkar%20and%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20had%20a%20similar%20opinion.%E2%80%9D%20(page%2090)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Malegaon%20in%20the%20autumn%20of%20that%20year%2C%20Savarkar%20felt%20that%20following%20the%20German%20example%20could%20solve%20Hindutva%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20problem%E2%80%99.%20This%20was%20just%20one%20example%20of%20several%20instances%20cited%20by%20the%20noted%20author%20where%20Savarkar%20justified%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20pogrom%20on%20the%20Jews.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20the%20book%20quotes%20Savarkar%20saying%20publicly%2C%20%E2%80%9CSurely%20Hitler%20knows%20better%20than%20Pandit%20Nehru%20does%20what%20suits%20Germany%20best.%20The%20very%20fact%20that%20Germany%20or%20Italy%20(under%20Mussolini)%20has%20so%20wonderfully%20recovered%20and%20grown%20so%20powerful%20as%20never%20before%20at%20the%20touch%20of%20Nazi%20or%20Fascist%20magical%20wand%20is%20enough%20to%20prove%20that%20those%20political%20%E2%80%98isms%E2%80%99%20were%20the%20most%20congenial%20tonics%20their%20health%20demanded.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECasolari%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CGolwalkar%20went%20further%20than%20Savarkar%20and%20even%20considered%20the%20possibility%20of%20denying%20the%20Muslims%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights.%20It%20is%20well-known%20that%20Golwalkar%E2%80%99s%20idea%20of%20nation%20was%20inspired%20by%20Johann%20Kaspar%20Bluntschli%2C%20%E2%80%98an%20exponent%20of%20German%20ethnic%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20and%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Theory%20of%20the%20State%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20to%20the%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20the%20Congress%20called%20for%20shunning%20violence%2C%20and%20also%20reiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20longstanding%20stand%20in%20support%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%20That%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20accused%20the%20Congress%20thereafter%20of%20supporting%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99%20(read%20Muslims)%20came%20across%20as%20a%20fitting%20parallel%20to%20what%20Savarkar%20and%20his%20ilk%20had%20stated%20to%20the%20anti-Nazi%20stand%20of%20the%20Congress%20of%20the%201930s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20began%20to%20escalate%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%20end%20up%20falling%20back%20on%C2%A0%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20line%20on%20Palestine%20but%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20campaign%20against%20Congress%20for%20that%20statement%20has%20continued%2C%20merely%20because%20it%20has%20an%20anti-Muslim%20edge%20to%20it%2C%20a%20potential%20weapon%20in%20a%20difficult%20election%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20many%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20attack%20is%20also%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20frequent%20attacks%20carried%20out%20on%20Jewish%20civilians%20by%20Arab%20militants%20infiltrating%20from%20neighbouring%20Syria%2C%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt%20in%20the%201950s%20and%20the%201960s%2C%20leading%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20to%20conduct%20raids%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Reprisal%20Operations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201955%2C%20David%20Ben-Gurion%2C%20considered%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20founding%20father%2C%20ordered%20one%20such%20raid%20against%20the%20Egyptians%20near%20Gaza%20after%20the%20murder%20of%20an%20Israeli%20civilian%20inside%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20his%20retirement%20from%20politics%2C%20though%2C%20Ben-Gurion%20famously%20went%20on%20to%20settle%20down%20at%20a%20modest%20house%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Negev%20desert%2C%20not%20very%20far%20from%20Gaza.%20Apart%20from%20a%20photo%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20what%20hung%20at%20his%20home%20was%20one%20other%20frame.%20It%20was%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20from%20India%2C%20a%20black%20and%20white%20visage%20of%20the%20ambassador%20of%20non-violence%20hanging%20from%20a%20wall%20of%20his%20small%20study.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20Savarkar%2C%20Hegdewar%20or%20Golwalkar.%20No%2C%20not%20even%20Nehru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20spotting%20that%20photo%20of%20Gandhi%20all%20those%20years%20ago%2C%20all%20the%20shame%20that%20I%20had%20felt%20on%20finding%20the%20Swastika%20at%20Yad%20Vesham%20vanished%20into%20the%20hot%20desert%20air%20of%20Negev.%20It%20was%20seamlessly%20replaced%20by%20the%20pride%20that%20only%20an%20Indian%20could%20feel.%20That%20a%20man%20whose%20lifetime%20had%20seen%20so%20much%20violence%20on%20his%20community%20had%20come%20home%20to%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697869423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21114244%2FUntitled-design-1-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fgandhi-ben-gurion-israel-india-hindutva-mohammed-zubair-kobbi-shoshani%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Israeli%20diplomat%20going%20after%20an%20award-winning%20fact%20checker%20seemed%20to%20have%20g